bat%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EIraq's%20first%20F-16s%20were%20delivered%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defensenews.com%2Fair%2F2015%2F07%2F13%2Fus-delivers-first-batch-of-f-16s-to-iraq%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%202015%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20became%20the%20mainstay%20of%20its%20air%20force%2C%20but%20within%20five%20years%20chronic%20maintenance%20and%20technical%20issues%20put%20their%20future%20into%20question.%20Nevertheless%2C%20in%20recent%20months%20the%20jets%20have%20become%20Iraq's%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thedrive.com%2Fthe-war-zone%2Firaqs-f-16-fleet-surges-in-importance-thanks-in-part-to-war-in-ukraine%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epremier%20strike%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20remnants%20of%20ISIS%20%E2%80%94%20in%20part%20because%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20has%20prevented%20Russia%20from%20supplying%20parts%20Iraq%20needs%20for%20its%20Russian-made%20helicopters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Iraq%20F-16%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b025a59751e3001929f98a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221077%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Iraqi%20F-16%20after%20delivery%20at%20Balad%20air%20base%20north%20of%20Baghdad%20in%20July%202015.%3Cp%3EAli%20Mohammed%2FAnadolu%20Agency%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EIt's%20unlikely%20Iraq%20wants%20the%20Rafale%20to%20supplement%20its%20larger%20F-16%20fleet%20in%20airstrikes%20against%20militants%20on%20the%20ground.%20Baghdad%20most%20likely%20wants%20the%20sleek%20French%20jet%20primarily%20for%20air%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EIraq%20already%20turned%20to%20France%20for%20long-range%20radar%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.janes.com%2Fdefence-news%2Fnews-detail%2Firaq-inaugurates-first-gm403-radar%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einaugurating%3C%2Fa%3E%20its%20first%20Thales%20Ground%20Master%20403%20in%20September%2C%20which%20is%20perhaps%20fitting%20since%20the%20KARI%20integrated%20air-defense%20system%20that%20France%20built%20for%20Iraq%20in%20the%20late%201980s%20was%20destroyed%20in%20the%20Gulf%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EWhile%20the%20F-16%20is%20a%20capable%20fighter%20for%20air%20defense%2C%20the%20US%20never%20sold%20Iraq%20the%20AIM-120%20air-to-air%20missile.%20Consequently%2C%20Iraq%20may%20hope%20that%20turning%20to%20France%20would%20give%20it%20a%20highly%20capable%20fighter%20armed%20with%20Meteor%20air-to-air%20missiles%2C%20greatly%20enhancing%20its%20limited%20air-defense%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EEgypt'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Es%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20Eagles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Egypt%20MiG-29%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b025dcc22d1a0019454c59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22767%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEgyptian%20Air%20Force%20MiG-29s%20during%20an%20exercise%20in%20Sudan%20in%20May%202021.%3Cp%3EASHRAF%20SHAZLY%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3ESince%20making%20peace%20with%20Israel%20in%201979%2C%20Egypt%20has%20primarily%20been%20a%20US%20arms%20client%2C%20amassing%20F-16s%2C%20AH-64%20attack%20helicopters%2C%20and%20M1%20tanks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20Egypt%20was%20never%20allowed%20buy%20F-15%20Eagles%20despite%20the%20US%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Farchive%2Fpolitics%2F1980%2F02%2F24%2Fus-will-supply-egypt-with-f15s-other-equipment%2F5f7284a8-54b9-434d-ae07-aeeab91c0afc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagreeing%20in%20principle%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20sell%20them%20and%20even%20though%20the%20US%20sold%20them%20to%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20Qatar%2C%20neither%20of%20which%20established%20diplomatic%20ties%20with%20Israel.%20In%202002%2C%20the%20US%20and%20Israel%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2F2002-01-01%2Fty-article%2Fisrael-u-s-understanding-egypt-will-not-get-f-16-fighter-plane%2F0000017f-f70c-d887-a7ff-ffeca6640000%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Breached%20a%20series%20of%20understandings%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20regarding%20US%20weapons%20sales%20to%20Egypt%2C%20one%20element%20of%20which%20was%20a%20ban%20on%20Egypt%20buying%20F-15s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EWhile%20Egypt%20did%20eventually%20acquire%20F-16s%20%E2%80%94%20it%20now%20has%20the%20world's%20fourth-largest%20fleet%20%E2%80%94%20it%20never%20got%20the%20AIM-120%2C%20severely%20limiting%20their%20air-defense%20capability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%3EHaving%20been%20denied%20the%20F-15%20for%20nearly%2040%20years%2C%20Egypt%20turned%20to%20Russia%2C%20ordering%20nearly%20four%20dozen%20MiG-29s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fukdefencejournal.org.uk%2Fegypt-buy-46-mig-29-combat-aircraft-2-billion-deal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efor%20%242%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202014%20and%20then%20two%20dozen%20Su-35s%20for%20%242%20billion%20in%202018.%20While%20the%20Russian%20jets%20couldn't%20exchange%20data%20with%20Egypt's%20US-made%20aircraft%2C%20Cairo%20hoped%20they%20could%20operate%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtoninstitute.org%2Fpolicy-analysis%2Funderstanding-egyptian-militarys-perspective-su-35-deal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bair%20force%20within%20an%20air%20force%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20partially%20redress%20its%20limited%20air-to-air%20capabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22127