s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20period%20was%20also%20matched%20by%20an%20international%20arms%20race%20in%20tech%2C%20characterized%20by%20expanded%20spending%2C%20fiscal%20support%20and%20a%20looser%20regulatory%20regime.%20The%20trend%20was%20further%20accelerated%20by%202020's%20pandemic%2C%20which%20pushed%20the%20need%20for%20these%20emerging%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20final%20factor%2C%20longer%20run-ups%20to%20tech%20IPOs%20meant%20that%20companies%20eventually%20debuted%20in%20public%20markets%20as%20mega-cap%20growth%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Has%20it%20happened%20before%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBofA%20cites%20a%20slew%20of%20bubbles%20that%20occurred%20through%20history%2C%20including%20speculation%20over%20tulips%20in%201700s%2C%20the%20Internet%20Bubble%20of%20the%2090s%2C%20and%20this%20century's%20housing%20and%20cryptocurrency%20frenzies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBubbles%20fueled%20by%20excessive%20leverage%2C%20democratization%20of%20markets%20and%20rampant%20speculation%20tend%20to%20end%20badly.%20But%20real%20disruptors%20can%20do%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20How%20is%20this%20different%20from%202000%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20point%20of%20comparison%20has%20been%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20of%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20which%20yielded%20a%20number%20of%20blue%20chip%20companies%20still%20traded%20today.%20But%20while%20that%20period%20ended%20in%20consolidation%20and%20some%20steep%20losses%20for%20investors%2C%20the%20current%20tech%20rally%20differs%20in%20an%20important%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday's%20top%20seven%20firms%20are%20much%20bigger%20than%20many%20tech%20firms%20in%202000%2C%20which%20signals%20that%20they%20can%20afford%20to%20deal%20with%20stiffer%20regulation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20deeper%20pockets%20mean%20companies%20can%20take%20greater%20advantage%20of%20the%20AI%20momentum%2C%20as%20it%20tends%20to%20favor%20fir