hopping%2040%2C000%20square%20feet%2C%20a%20house%20that%20size%20requires%20a%20level%20of%20detail%20and%20attention%20in%20its%20upkeep%20that%20two%20people%20alone%20can't%20provide%20(especially%20if%20they're%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbeyonce-renaissance-world-tour-best-photos-opening-night-2023-5%5C%22%3Ebusy%20touring%20the%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20their%20newest%20album.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20homes%20run%20like%20a%20well-oiled%20machine%2C%26quot%3B%20Jenny%20Greenwood%20Huber%2C%20owner%20and%20founder%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fheritage-em.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHeritage%20Estate%20Management%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAt%20this%20level%2C%20it's%20usually%20a%20business%20in%20its%20own%20right.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22640%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20professional%20picture%20of%20a%20woman%20on%20the%20beach.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b199e19751e300192a2c3a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJenny%20Greenwood%20Huber%2C%20founder%20and%20owner%20of%20Heritage%20Estate%20Management.%3Cp%3EHeritage%20Estate%20Management%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHeritage%20Estate%20Management%20provides%20household%20staffing%20and%20property%20management%20services%20for%20West%20Coast%20estates%20in%20places%20like%20Beverly%20Hills%20and%20Malibu%2C%20where%20the%20Carters'%20new%20home%20is%20located.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20staffing%2C%20that%20means%20hiring%20full-time%20employees%20to%20keep%20a%20home%20in%20pristine%20condition.%20Think%20Downton%20Abbey%20for%20the%2021st%20century%3A%20Butlers%20to%20help%20oversee%20all%20operations%20like%20housekeeping%20and%20entertaining%20on%20the%20premises%2C%20as%20well%20as%20serving%20the%20homeowners%20and%20their%20guests%3B%20nannies%20who%20fo