at%20it's%20worth%20taking%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20particularly%20if%20it's%20far%20away.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20at%20a%20minimum%2C%20he%20said%20drivers%20should%20make%20sure%20they're%20earning%20at%20least%20%241%20to%20%241.50%20a%20mile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird%3A%20Focus%20on%20maintaining%20a%20strong%20rating%2C%20acceptance%20rate%2C%20and%20completion%20rate.%20Coleman%20has%20a%2070%25%20acceptance%20rate%2C%20a%2093%25%20completion%20rate%2C%20and%20a%204.98%20rating.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20tried%20to%20accept%2070%25%20of%20the%20orders%20that%20are%20given%20to%20me%20every%20hour%20because%20it%20helps%20you%20with%20your%20ratings%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHigher%20ratings%20can%20lead%20to%20better%20opportunities%20and%20those%20opportunities%20can%20turn%20into%20better%20earnings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFourth%3A%20Even%20if%20it%20won't%20always%20result%20in%20a%20great%20tip%2C%20Coleman%20said%20providing%20great%20customer%20service%20is%20important%20for%20getting%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-eats-driver-how-to-get-good-tips-stay-safe-2023-5%5C%22%3Ekeeping%20a%20high%20rating%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20said%20he%20tries%20to%20update%20customers%20on%20their%20order%20status%20consistently%2C%20and%20in%20the%20case%20of%20grocery%20deliveries%2C%20allows%20them%20to%20choose%20a%20replacement%20when%20an%20item%20is%20unavailable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20treat%20every%20delivery%20I%20accept%20as%20if%20I%20was%20ordering%20it%20myself%2C%26quot%3B%20he%C2%A0said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20Coleman%20said%20he%20has%20no%20plans%20to%20leave%20Hawaii%2C%20and%20that%20he%20hopes%20to%20put%20the%20money%20he's%20been%20saving%20up%20towards%20some%20entrepreneurial%20endeavors%20someday.%20He%20said%20the%20only%20downsides%20to%20doing%20DoorDash%20in%20the%20Aloha%20State%20are%20the%20traffic%20and%20the%20number%20of%20one