t-storm-stretches-into-southern-europe-health-alerts-issued%2Famp_articleshow%2F101801046.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Faced%20With%20an%20Opposition%20Coming%20Together%2C%20BJP%20Tries%20to%20Balance%20the%20Optics%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20180922%2FFwkAAXcWcAQg8uV.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20as%2024%20opposition%20parties%20are%20set%20to%20meet%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20July%2017%20and%2018%20to%20finalise%20the%20contours%20of%20a%20united%20opposition%20front%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20too%2C%20has%20called%20for%20a%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20meeting%20on%20July%2018.%20The%20NDA%20meet%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20move%20to%20offset%20the%20attention%20the%20opposition%20forces%20have%20been%20getting%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20forces%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20find%20common%20ground%20to%20launch%20a%20united%20campaign%20against%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20ahead%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20polls.%20The%20first%20such%20concerted%20attempt%20was%20made%20on%20June%2023%20in%20Patna%20when%2C%20barring%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20all%20opposition%20parties%20pledged%20to%20chalk%20out%20a%20common%20minimum%20agenda%20for%20the%20opposition%20front.%20The%20AAP%20had%20then%20insisted%20that%20it%20could%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20united%20opposition%20front%20only%20when%20the%20Congress%20formally%20opposed%20the%20controversial%20central%20ordinance%20which%20overturned%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20establishing%20powers%20of%20the%20elected%20Delhi%20government%20over%20the%20Delhi%20bureaucracy.%20The%20Congress%2C%20after%20an%20initial%20flip-flop%20over%20the%20ordinance%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20blinked%20ahead%20of%20the%20Bengaluru%20meet.%20K.C.%20Venugopal%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20general%20secretary%20(organisation)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fahead-of-second-opposition-meet-congress-says-it-will-not-support-delhi-ordinance%5C%22%3Eon%20Sunday%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20will%20oppose%20the%20ordinance%20in%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%20beginning%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Modi%20May%20Dismiss%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20Efforts%20To%20Unite%2C%20but%20They%20Are%20Borne%20Out%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hegemony%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmodi-dismiss-oppositions-unity-bjp-hegemony%5C%22%3EModi%20May%20Dismiss%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20Efforts%20To%20Unite%2C%20but%20They%20Are%20Borne%20Out%20of%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hegemony%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVenugopal%E2%80%99s%20statement%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20yet%20another%20step%20by%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20to%20conjure%20up%20as%20big%20an%20opposition%20front%20as%20possible%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20joining%20ranks%20with%20arch%20rivals%20who%20are%20opposed%20to%20the%20BJP.%20With%20AAP%20now%20likely%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20opposition%20meeting%2C%20the%20two-day%20congregation%20of%20non-BJP%20parties%20is%20all%20set%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20common%20minimum%20agenda%20and%20possibly%20an%20implementable%20seat-sharing%20formula%20in%20different%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20moved%20from%20one%20goal%20post%20to%20another.%20Following%20its%20big%20victory%20in%202019%2C%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP%20has%20been%20unsparing%20with%20its%20allies%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20complete%20disintegration%20of%20the%20NDA.%20Formidable%20allies%20like%20the%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%2C%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20other%20smaller%20parties%20have%20left%20the%20NDA%20one%20by%20one%20through%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20second%20tenure%20as%20the%20prime%20minister.%20However%2C%20the%20humiliating%20defeat%20in%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20Punjab%20and%20more%20recently%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20has%20made%20the%20BJP%20sit%20up%20and%20think%20about%20forging%20a%20pre-poll%20coalition%20to%20challenge%20the%20opposition%20front.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUntil%20recently%2C%20several%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20had%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20a%20pre-poll%20coalition%20to%20win%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20However%2C%20a%20string%20of%20failures%20in%20assembly%20elections%20has%20seemingly%20made%20them%20re-strategise%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20party%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20regional%20parties%20like%20the%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu-led%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20H.D.%20Kumaraswamy-led%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Sukhbir%20Badal-led%20Akali%20Dal%20in%20Punjab%2C%20and%20smaller%20caste-based%20outfits%20led%20by%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20Jitan%20Ram%20Manjhi%2C%20Chirag%20Paswan%20and%20Mukesh%20Sahni%2C%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Om%20Prakash%20Rajbhar%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Pawan%20Kalyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClearly%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20confidence%20has%20dwindled%20after%20the%20Karnataka%20assembly%20elections%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Congress%20handed%20it%20a%20comprehensive%20defeat.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20defeat%20has%20also%20possibly%20come%20as%20a%20realisation%20that%20the%20BJP%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20able%20to%20expand%20its%20territorial%20footprint%20at%20all%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20second%20tenure.%20It%20has%20lost%20the%20only%20southern%20state%20Karnataka%2C%20while%20its%20presence%20in%20states%20like%20Telangana%2C%20Odisha%20and%20West%20Bengal%20%E2%80%93%20where%20it%20put%20up%20a%20surprisingly%20good%20show%20in%20the%202019%20polls%20%E2%80%93%20has%20only%20become%20weaker.%20Nitish%20Kumar%20and%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%E2%80%99s%20exit%20from%20the%20NDA%20has%20further%20affected%20its%20electoral%20prospects%20in%20Bihar%20and%20Odisha.%20The%20way%20the%20saffron%20party%20welcomed%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20faction%20of%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20into%20its%20fold%20indicates%20its%20weak%20footing%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20all%20opposition%20parties%20had%20united%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22A%20Look%20at%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20Lost%20Elections%20and%20Broken%20Alliances%20Amid%20Talks%20on%20Lack%20of%20Opposition%20Unity%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fa-look-at-the-ndas-lost-elections-and-broken-alliances-amid-talks-on-lack-of-opposition-unity%5C%22%3EA%20Look%20at%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20Lost%20Elections%20and%20Broken%20Alliances%20Amid%20Talks%20on%20Lack%20of%20Opposition%20Unity%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindi%20heartland%20is%20the%20only%20bastion%20where%20the%20BJP%20is%20still%20on%20a%20strong%20wicket%2C%20especially%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20which%20has%2080%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20The%20exit%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar%20from%20the%20MVA%20in%20Maharashtra%20with%2048%20seats%20has%20undoubtedly%20improved%20the%20NDA%E2%80%99s%20prospects.%20But%20these%20alone%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20cross%20the%20majority%20mark.%20Precisely%20because%20of%20such%20factors%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20that%20prided%20itself%20on%20its%20electoral%20strength%2C%20is%20looking%20to%20refuel%20the%20NDA%20by%20reaching%20out%20to%20older%20allies%20that%20it%20had%20no%20hesitation%20in%20deserting%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20holding%20the%20NDA%20gathering%20to%20take%20the%20sheen%20away%20from%20the%20opposition%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20hog%20media%20attention%20and%20keep%20the%20electoral%20race%20competitive.%20Beyond%20the%20optics%2C%20however%2C%20the%20NDA%20remains%20a%20much%20smaller%20coalition%20than%20the%20opposition%20front%20in%20the%20making%2C%20with%20the%20BJP%20as%20the%20only%20formidable%20political%20force%20in%20the%20alliance.%20By%20the%20sheer%20virtue%20of%20its%20dominance%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20still%20emerge%20as%20a%20winner%20in%20the%20final%20run.%20Yet%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20authoritarianism%20has%20brought%20traditional%20rivals%20in%20the%20opposition%20ranks%20together%2C%20even%20as%20it%20remains%20too%20distant%20from%20becoming%20a%20truly%20pan-Indian%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689505257000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20180922%2FFwkAAXcWcAQg8uV.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffaced-with-an-opposition-coming-together-bjp-tries-to-balance-the-optics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Until%20recently%2C%20several%20top%20BJP%20leaders%20had%20expressed%20confidence%20that%20the%20saffron%20party%20didn%E2%80%99t%20need%20a%20pre-poll%20coalition%20to%20win%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20However%2C%20a%20string%20of%20failures%20in%20assembly%20elections%20has%20seemingly%20made%20them%20re-strategise.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffaced-with-an-opposition-coming-together-bjp-tries-to-balance-the-optics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I'm%20a%20millennial%20real-estate%20agent%20here%20to%20tell%20you%20that%20long-term%20homeownership%20is%20not%20the%20best%20way%20to%20build%20wealth.%20Here's%20why.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223023%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20Ravitz%20and%20his%20wife%20at%20an%20event.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b03201c22d1a0019454f7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20Ravitz%20and%20his%20wife%20plan%20to%20fix%20and%20flip%20homes%20indefinitely.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20David%20Ravitz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EDavid%20Ravitz%20thinks%20he's%20cracked%20the%20code%20to%20building%20wealth%20with%20homeownership.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERavitz%20bought%20a%20home%20in%202021%2C%20lived%20in%20it%20during%20renovations%2C%20and%20is%20selling%20it%20two%20years%20later.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20strength%20of%20the%20Boca%20Raton%2C%20Florida%2C%20market%20provides%20a%20tailwind%20for%20his%20current%20investment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20David%20Ravitz%2C%2031%2C%20a%20millennial%20real-estate%20agent%20who%20is%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Edropping%20the%20idea%20of%20long-term%20homeownership%20to%20accumulate%20wealth.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20and%20lived%20in%20the%20same%20house%20for%2018%20years.%20But%20most%20people%20don't%20stay%20in%20the%20same%20home%20for%20more%20than%2010%20years%20anymore%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20they%20are%20more%20inclined%20to%20move%20around%20and%20sell.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20similar%20to%20the%20workforce.%20You%20don't%20see%20people%20working%20at%20the%20same%20company%20for%2025%20or%2030%20years.%20Instead%2C%20we%20jump%20around%20to%20different%20companies%20or%20industries%20for%20better%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20moving%20around%20means%20the%20American%20dream%20of%20homeownership%20is%20changing%2C%20and%20that's%20not%20necessarily%20a%20bad%20thing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20giving%20up%20on%20long-term%20homeownership%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20in%20finance%20for%20a%20number%20of%20years.%20I%20went%20back%20to%20school%20and%20got%20my%20MBA%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Miami%2C%20and%20then%20jumped%20into%20real%20estate.%20I'm%20going%20on%20four%20years%20now%20as%20a%20real%20estate%20agent%20in%20South%20Florida.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20Ravitz%20and%20his%20wife.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b033939751e3001929fdd2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222274%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20Ravitz%20and%20his%20wife.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20David%20Ravitz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEveryday%2C%20I%20look%20at%2C%20and%20buy%20and%20sell%20houses%20on%20behalf%20of%20my%20clients.%20So%2C%20I'm%20in%20tune%20with%20the%20market%20and%20have%20a%20keen%20perspective%20on%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20housing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20the%20South%20Florida%20real-estate%20market%20has%20taken%20off%20and%20there%20has%20been%20a%20flood%20of%20people%20moving%20here.%20You%20hear%20about%20prices%20leveling%20out%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20but%20we%20haven't%20seen%20that%20at%20all%20in%20this%20area.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20purchased%20our%20first%20house%20for%20%24960%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20a%20four-bedroom%2C%20three-bathroom%2C%20ranch%20style%20starter-home%20in%20Boca%20Raton.%20The%20home%20had%20really%20good%20bones%20but%20was%20built%20in%201996%20and%20needed%20to%20be%20updated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20we%20thought%20we%20would%20renovate%20the%20home%20and%20live%20there%20for%20at%20least%20four%20years%20before%20selling.%20However%2C%20given%20the%20strength%20of%20the%20area's%20market%2C%20our%20mentality%20shifted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20maximize%20our%20investment%2C%20we%20moved%20into%20the%20home%20and%20renovated%20it%20over%20the%20course%20of%20two%20years%2C%20and%20have%20now%20listed%20the%20property%20for%20sale.%20We%20plan%20on%20repeating%20that%20process%20indefinitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe're%20not%20traditional%20fix%20and%20flippers%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20in%20the%20wealth%20accumulation%20phase%20of%20our%20life%20and%20believe%20this%20model%20will%20yield%20the%20most%20results%20financially.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20advantage%20of%20this%20model%20is%20from%20a%20tax%20perspective.%20If%20you're%20a%20married%20couple%20and%20you%20own%20a%20home%20as%20a%20primary%20residence%20for%20at%20least%20two%20years%2C%20you%20can%20have%20tax-free%20capital%20gains%20up%20to%20%24500%2C000.%20If%20you're%20single%2C%20that%20total%20is%20up%20to%20%24250%2C000.%20That%20tax%20treatment%20provides%20opportunity%20for%20investment%20because%20you%20build%20equity%20and%20the%20home%20appreciates%20as%20it%20is%20renovated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20Ravitz's%20renovated%20kitchen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b0331fc22d1a0019454ff9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDavid%20Ravitz's%20renovated%20kitchen.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20David%20Ravitz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20definitely%20depends%20on%20the%20route%20that%20you%20go%2C%20but%20I%20think%20this%20renovation%20approach%20can%20work%20in%20any%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20believe%20our%20home%20purchase%20in%20Boca%20Raton%20is%20a%20good%20investment%20due%20to%20the%20demand%20for%20housing%20in%20the%20area.%20Prices%20are%20elevated%20while%20supplies%20are%20constrained%2C%20and%20there%20are%20tons%20of%20people%20looking%20to%20jump%20into%20the%20market.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20plan%20to%20repeat%20this%20process%20indefinitely%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20us%20two%20years%20and%20%24500%2C000%20to%20fully%20renovate%20our%20home.%20We%20expanded%20floor%20plans%20and%20brought%20in%20new%20appliances%20and%20furniture.%20In%20June%2C%20we%20put%20it%20on%20the%20market%20for%20just%20under%20%242%20million.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20budgeted%20for%20the%20home's%20renovation%20by%20looking%20at%20other%20remodeled%20homes%20in%20our%20area.%20To%20make%20sure%20we%20saved%20on%20the%20project%2C%20I%20used%20Excel%20spreadsheets%20to%20keep%20track%20of%20costs.%20Since%20we%20were%20living%20in%20the%20home%2C%20I%20was%20also%20able%20to%20observe%20our%20contractors%20and%20make%20sure%20we%20splurged%20where%20we%20wanted%20and%20saved%20where%20we%20needed.%20We%20stayed%20right%20on%20budget%20almost%20to%20the%20dollar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22David%20Ravitz's%20renovated%20home.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b032f5c22d1a0019454fcc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221366%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20renovated%20dining%20area%20in%20David%20Ravitz's%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20David%20Ravitz.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20has%20been%20listed%20for%20a%20month%20but%20buyers%20have%20been%20pretty%20active%20%E2%80%94%20we've%20received%20numerous%20offers.%20I%20anticipate%20it%20will%20sell%20in%20August%20or%20September.%20But%20no%20matter%C2%A0how%20long%20it%20takes%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20are%20not%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20sell%20%E2%80%94%20we%20love%20living%20here%20and%20know%20our%20investment%20will%20pay%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20we%20plan%20to%20target%20another%20home%20and%20repeat%20the%20process%20all%20over%20again.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agent-rejects-long-term-homeownership-to-build-wealth-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689505200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b03210c22d1a0019454f89%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A