.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Celebrating%20Kerala's%20Renaissance%20Man%2C%20M.T.%20Vasudevan%20Nair%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16150754%2F1280px-M_T_Vasudevan_Nair.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSee%2C%20this%20is%20how%20a%20%E2%80%98child%20of%20%3Cem%3EKarkitakam%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20becomes%20%3Cem%3Ekismet%E2%80%99s%3C%2Fem%3E%20(destiny%E2%80%99s)%20child.%20Or%20rather%2C%20it%20is%20a%20rarest%20of%20rare%20classical%20instance%20of%20such%20a%20turnaround.%E2%80%9D%20This%20was%20how%20N.%20Gopala%20Krishnan%20(NGK%2C%20as%20his%20friends%20call%20him)%2C%20writer%2C%20translator%20and%20erstwhile%20senior%20administrator%20in%20government%20services%2C%20referred%20to%20the%20media%20coverage%20of%20the%2080th%20birthday%20celebrations%20of%20M.T.%20Vasudevan%20Nair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comment%20was%20made%20in%20a%20private%20conversation%20in%202013%20at%20Kozhikode%2C%20the%20coastal%20town%20in%20north%20Kerala%20where%20NGK%20and%20MT%20resided.%20NGK%20was%20known%20to%20have%20a%20penchant%20for%20adding%20some%20flourish%20or%20a%20bit%20of%20allegory%20to%20normal%2C%20everyday%20conversations.%20Sometimes%2C%20these%20verbal%20exercises%20were%20so%20involved%20that%20they%20used%20to%20go%20above%20the%20heads%20of%20those%20who%20were%20being%20addressed.%20But%2C%20the%20allegory%20in%20his%20comment%20on%20MT%20was%20not%20lost%20on%20the%20audience.%20All%20of%20us%20were%20from%20Kerala%20and%20we%20understood%20what%20Karkitakam%20and%20kismet%20meant%20in%20Malayalam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarkitakam%2C%20the%20harshest%20of%20harsh%20monsoon%20months%20was%20synonymous%20with%20penury%20and%20privation%20in%20Kerala.%20Kismet%2C%20a%20word%20shared%20by%20many%20Indian%20languages%20meant%20good%20luck%20or%20positive%20destiny.%20NGK%E2%80%99s%20one-liner%20captures%20MT%E2%80%99s%20journey%20from%20being%20a%20deprived%20child%20to%20an%20advanced%20age%20with%20tremendous%20material%20and%20intellectual%20successes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENGK%20was%20not%20in%20the%20habit%20of%20explaining%20his%20allegories.%20However%2C%20on%20this%20occasion%2C%20the%20English%20translator%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20last%20novel%20%3Cem%3EVaranasi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(published%20in%202003)%2C%20followed%20up%20his%20combination%20of%20%E2%80%9CKarkitakam%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ckismet%E2%80%9D%20with%20a%20sort%20of%20solemn%20elucidation.%20He%20said%20that%20MT%E2%80%99s%20life%20as%20well%20as%20his%20birthdays%20have%20a%20trajectory%20marked%20by%20great%20gains%2C%20but%20this%20journey%20was%20by%20no%20means%20smooth%20or%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20reach%20where%20he%20has%2C%20MT%20had%20to%20draw%20copiously%20not%20only%20from%20his%20innate%20and%20vast%20creativity%2C%20but%20also%20go%20through%20sordid%20ordeals%20characterised%20by%20strenuous%20and%20sustained%20physical%20labour.%20It%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20an%20onerous%20journey%20for%20the%20mind%20and%20the%20body.%E2%80%9D%20NGK%20passed%20away%20in%202014%20but%20eight%20years%20later%2C%20in%202022%2C%20his%20allegory%20came%20back%20to%20my%20mind%20when%20I%20read%20about%20yet%20another%20MT%20birthday%20in%20the%20Kerala%20newspapers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJuly%2014%2C%202022.%20On%20this%20day%2C%20MT%20started%20yet%20another%20journey%20by%20road%2C%20from%20his%20house%20in%20Kozhikode%20to%20the%20Malankara%20hills%20in%20central%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Thodupuzha.%20A%20journey%20of%20about%20250%20kilometres%20is%20not%20usually%20very%20long%20but%20it%20is%20arduous%20in%20this%20South%20Indian%20state%20during%20the%20monsoon%20marked%20by%20sporadic%20rains%20of%20varying%20intensity.%20The%20highways%20of%20Kerala%20have%20some%20notoriously%20rough%20patches%20too%2C%20especially%20while%20going%20up%20the%20hills%20of%20Thodupuzha%E2%80%99s%20Malanad%20regions.%20The%20strict%20restrictions%20on%20travel%20and%20social%20interactions%20that%20were%20imposed%20off%20and%20on%20in%20the%20state%20since%20March%202019%2C%20on%20account%20of%20the%20COVID%20pandemic%2C%20were%20in%20force%20until%20the%20second%20week%20of%20July%202022.%20Still%2C%20not%20many%20senior%20citizens%20are%20venturing%20out%20to%20travel%2C%20especially%20by%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20official%20records%2C%20on%20July%2015%2C%20the%20very%20next%20day%20of%20his%20journey%2C%20MT%20would%20complete%2089%20years%20of%20age.%20By%20normal%20%E2%80%9Csenior%20citizen%E2%80%9D%20standards%2C%20the%20trip%20would%20have%20been%20quite%20daunting.%20But%2C%20MT%20was%20not%20the%20one%20to%20be%20deterred%20by%20the%20multiple%20factors%20that%20would%20have%20limited%20other%20elders%E2%80%99%20wish%20to%20travel.%20A%20couple%20of%20months%20before%20the%20journey%2C%20he%20was%20afflicted%20with%20various%20ailments%20%E2%80%93%20high%20fever%20and%20chest%20congestion%2C%20which%20would%2C%20presumably%2C%20have%20had%20a%20relatively%20serious%20impact%20given%20his%20long-standing%20diabetes%20and%20unremitting%20%E2%80%98beedi%E2%80%99%20smoking.%20But%2C%20as%20has%20been%20his%20wont%20over%20several%20decades%2C%20MT%20seemed%20to%20have%20overcome%20the%20physical%20strains%20caused%20by%20the%20ailments%20by%20taking%20adequate%20medication%20and%20drawing%20up%20on%20his%20self-generated%20energy%20and%20will%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151104%2FKeralaliteraturefestival_08681.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151104%2FKeralaliteraturefestival_08681.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151104%2FKeralaliteraturefestival_08681-300x200.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663455%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EM.%20T.%20Vasudevan%20Nair.%20at%20the%20Kerala%20literature%20festival%20in%202016.%20Photo%3A%20Amarjith%20Mohan%2FWikimedia%20commons%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%2C%20he%20left%20Kozhikode%20that%20morning%2C%20took%20a%20short%20break%20for%20lunch%20at%20the%20central%20Kerala%20town%20of%20Thrissur%2C%20and%20went%20up%20the%20hills%20to%20reach%20Thodupuzha%20by%20the%20evening.%20Thankfully%2C%20the%20rains%20had%20not%20hindered%20his%20progress%20through%20the%20day.%20He%20joined%20daughter%20Aswathy%20at%20Thodupuzha%2C%20who%20had%20been%20camping%20there%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%20to%20oversee%20the%20production%20of%20one%20of%20the%20episodes%20of%20a%20nine-part%20OTT%20anthology%20movie%20series%20based%20on%20stories%20written%20by%20MT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20on%20July%2015%2C%20MT%20joined%20the%20film%20crew%20at%20the%20shooting%20location%20around%20noon.%20Prominent%20film%20director%20Priyadarshan%20and%20internationally%20renowned%20actor%20Mohanlal%2C%20who%20were%20part%20of%20the%20project%2C%20welcomed%20MT.%20A%20birthday%20celebration%20of%20sorts%20followed%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccutting%20the%20cake%E2%80%9D%20ceremony%20and%20the%20traditional%20Kerala%20%3Cem%3Esadya%3C%2Fem%3E%20(feast).%20A%20very%20unique%20form%20of%20nostalgia%20has%20often%20been%20a%20prominent%20characteristic%20of%20the%20Malayalis%E2%80%99%20socio-cultural%20life%20and%20naturally%20MT%E2%80%99s%20literature%20has%20time%20and%20again%20captured%20and%20reflected%20this%20trait.%20Nostalgia%20was%20an%20overwhelming%20sensation%20for%20almost%20everybody%20on%20the%20sets%20that%20day%2C%20for%20different%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENostalgia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20MT%2C%20the%20story%20being%20filmed%20was%20a%20revisit%20to%20his%20yesteryear.%20It%20was%20%3Cem%3EOlavum%20Threeravum%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Ripples%20and%20Shores)%2C%20which%20had%20been%20originally%20made%20into%20a%20movie%20in%201969.%20MT%E2%80%99s%20screenplay%20was%20then%20directed%20by%20legendary%20Malayalam%20filmmaker%20P.N%20Menon.%20The%20lead%20role%20was%20played%20by%20Madhu%2C%20one%20of%20the%20icons%20of%20Malayalam%20cinema.%20Over%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20writing%20in%20a%20prominent%20Malayalam%20daily%2C%20Priyadarshan%20had%20described%20MT%20as%20the%20personal%20pride%20of%20every%20Malayali.%20In%20the%20same%20breath%20he%20declared%20that%20the%20desire%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmake%20a%20film%20on%20something%20written%20by%20MT%E2%80%9D%20was%20the%20most%20intense%20creative%20urge%20that%20he%20had%20ever%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20career%20as%20a%20cinema%20director%20had%20begun%20in%20Kerala%20with%20the%20Malayalam%20film%20industry%2C%20but%20in%20due%20course%2C%20he%20had%20moved%20on%20to%20a%20successful%20career%20in%20other%20languages%20and%20film%20industries%20too%2C%20including%20Hindi%20and%20Tamil.%20He%20was%20a%20much%20sought%20after%20director%2C%20but%20he%20himself%20had%20described%20the%20%E2%80%9Cabsence%20of%20an%20MT%20film%E2%80%9D%20as%20%E2%80%9Ca%20choking%20void%E2%80%9D%20in%20his%20career.%20Finally%2C%20Priyadarshan%20was%20getting%20to%20fill%20that%20void.%20As%20for%20Mohanlal%2C%20the%20protagonist%20in%20the%20MT%20movie%2C%20some%20of%20the%20stellar%20characters%20that%20helped%20him%20make%20a%20mark%20in%20the%20movies%20through%20a%20career%20lasting%20for%20over%20four%20decades%20were%20written%20by%20MT.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThus%20the%20Thodupuzha%20episode%20of%20July%2014%20and%2015%2C%202022%20involving%20other%20creative%20giants%20of%20Malayalam%20cinema%2C%20was%20a%20microcosm%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20own%20life%20and%20journey%20that%20saw%20the%20transformation%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9CKarkitakam%E2%80%99s%20child%20into%20a%20destiny%E2%80%99s%20child%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Son%20of%20Karikitakam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarkitakam%20is%20the%20month%20of%20intense%20rain%20lasting%20for%20days%20on%20end.%20Dark%20rain%20clouds%20dominate%20the%20skies%20almost%20perennially%20during%20this%20month.%20In%20the%20olden%20times%2C%20the%20rain%20and%20the%20dark%20atmosphere%20created%20by%20it%20practically%20put%20a%20stop%20to%20all%20human%20activity%2C%20including%20professional%20engagements.%20So%20much%20so%2C%20the%20month%20was%20synonymous%20with%20deprivation%20and%20Malayalis%20feared%20this%20leanest%20of%20lean%20months%20the%20most.%20Throughout%20this%20month%2C%20Kerala%20reverberates%20with%20the%20ritualistic%20daily%20reading%20of%20the%20Ramayana.%20Indeed%2C%20divine%20powers%20are%20invoked%20to%20drive%20away%20the%20gloom%2C%20the%20fear%20and%20the%20ill-effects%20of%20the%20season%20of%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20early%20birthdays%20as%20well%20as%20the%20early%20childhood%20that%20Vasu%20(as%20MT%20was%20called%20at%20home)%20had%2C%20in%20many%20ways%2C%20corroborated%20the%20sobriquet%20of%20%E2%80%9CKarkitakam%E2%80%99s%20child%E2%80%9D.%20His%20mother%20Ammalu%20Amma%20had%20serious%20health%20issues%20while%20carrying%20him%20in%20her%20womb.%20There%20was%20even%20a%20medical%20advice%20to%20terminate%20the%20pregnancy.%20This%20was%20attempted%2C%20but%20the%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%20did%20not%20succeed.%20Then%2C%20Ammalu%20Amma%20had%20wanted%20a%20girl%20after%20having%20given%20birth%20to%20three%20sons.%20Thus%20Vasu%20was%20essentially%20an%20%E2%80%9Cunwanted%20and%20accidental%E2%80%9D%20child.%20His%20father%20T%20Narayanan%20Nair%20was%20employed%20in%20Ceylon%20and%20was%20not%20present%20at%20the%20time%20of%20his%20birth.%20Vasu%20would%20see%20him%20for%20the%20first%20time%20only%20after%20he%20had%20crossed%20the%20age%20of%20two.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMT%E2%80%99s%20three%20elders%20brothers%20%E2%80%93%20M.T.%20Govindan%20Nair%2C%20M.T.%20Balakrishnan%20Nair%20and%20M.T.%20Narayanan%20Nair%20%E2%80%93%20as%20well%20as%20many%20of%20his%20relatives%20have%20recorded%20that%20his%20early%20childhood%20was%20very%20much%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20dark%20and%20uncertain%20elements%20associated%20with%20the%20month%20of%20Karkitakam.%20According%20to%20his%20brothers%2C%20he%20was%20an%20obstinate%20kid%20craving%20for%20attention%20and%20was%20extremely%20difficult%2C%20almost%20rebelliously%20delinquent.%20The%20economic%20travails%20of%20the%20family%20as%20well%20as%20the%20absentee%20father%20working%20in%20far%20off%20lands%20added%20to%20the%20sense%20of%20alienation%20that%20the%20young%20MT%20had.%20MT%20himself%20has%20recorded%20that%2C%20as%20a%20child%2C%20he%20did%20feel%20a%20sense%20of%20loss%20at%20not%20getting%20the%20father%E2%80%99s%20affection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVasu%E2%80%99s%20stubbornness%20had%20many%20manifestations%20in%20his%20difficult%20childhood.%20His%20brother%20MTB%20Nair%20recorded%20as%20follows%20in%20an%20article.%20%E2%80%9CHe%20(Vasu)%20would%20cry%20lying%20on%20the%20bed%20when%20he%20woke%20up.%20When%20he%20realised%20crying%20was%20not%20helping%20him%20get%20attention%2C%20he%20would%20come%20to%20the%20kitchen.%20Mother%20would%20have%20work%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20He%20would%20beat%20her.%20She%20would%20strike%20him%20back%20when%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20tolerate%20it%20any%20longer.%20Then%20it%20was%20over.%20He%20would%20beat%20mother%2C%20pinch%20and%20scratch%20her.%20He%20would%20tear%20the%20clothes%20she%20was%20wearing.%20Such%20was%20the%20vehemence%20in%20his%20actions%20that%20people%20who%20came%20home%20would%20wonder%3A%20Oh%20my!%20Why%20does%20this%20child%20behave%20in%20such%20manner!%20What%20does%20sister%20Ammalu%20do%20with%20him%3F%20I%20have%20heard%20mother%20tell%20them%2C%20it%20is%20an%20age%20where%20he%20needs%20affection%20and%20care.%20Do%20I%20have%20time%20for%20it%3F%20Is%20there%20anyone%20here%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMT%E2%80%99s%20birthdays%20came%20and%20went%20but%20were%20never%20celebrated%20in%20childhood.%20The%20birthdays%20of%20his%20brothers%20were%20also%20treated%20with%20same%20indifference%20by%20the%20larger%20family.%20Normally%2C%20the%20sweet%20dish%20called%20%3Cem%3Epayasam%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20made%20in%20Malayali%20households%20to%20celebrate%20birthdays%2C%20but%20the%20MT%20brothers%20never%20experienced%20this%20pleasant%20culinary%20gift%20in%20their%20childhoods.%20In%20the%20matrilineal%20system%20of%20household%20governance%20that%20existed%20in%20the%20Nair%20households%20such%20as%20MT%E2%80%99s%20during%20that%20period%2C%20the%20controls%20of%20the%20treasury%20and%20granary%20were%20with%20the%20uncles%2C%20who%20allocated%20whatever%20meagre%20supplies%20of%20rice%20and%20other%20essentials%20that%20they%20deemed%20fit%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20family.%20Any%20request%20for%20enhancement%20of%20supplies%20was%20met%20with%20severe%20opprobrium.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMT%20has%20written%20a%20semi-fictional%20account%20on%20a%20birthday%20situation%20of%20yore.%20The%20story%20titled%20%3Cem%3EOru%20Pirannalinte%20Orma%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0(Memory%20of%20a%20Birthday)%20shows%20his%20mother%20fainting%20after%20being%20beaten%20by%20her%20brother%20for%20asking%20extra%20quantity%20of%20rice%20for%20making%20payasam.%20While%20creating%20this%20fictional%20narrative%20loosely%20based%20on%20a%20real%20incident%2C%20MT%20deftly%20delineated%20some%20contours%20of%20his%20depressive%20childhood.%20In%20the%20same%20narrative%2C%20however%2C%20MT%20also%20recorded%20some%20other%20developments%20of%20the%20time%20in%20which%20the%20story%20was%20written%2C%20where%20a%20person%2C%20who%20is%20evidently%20much%20in%20love%20with%20him%2C%20wrote%20as%20follows%3A%20%E2%80%9CYour%20birthday%20is%20on%20the%20next%20Thursday.%20You%20should%20have%20your%20breakfast%20only%20after%20a%20morning%20bath.%20It%20is%20a%20good%20omen%20that%20it%20is%20Thursday.%20I%20am%20offering%20%3Cem%3EDhara%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20Payasam%20(special%20prayers%20and%20sacred%20sweet%20to%20propitiate%20God)%20at%20the%20Shiva%20temple%E2%80%9D.%20This%20narrative%20shows%20that%20finally%2C%20there%20are%20people%20who%20not%20only%20remember%20his%20birthday%20but%20observe%20it%20quietly%20through%20prayers%20and%20offerings%20to%20god.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approbation%20of%20his%20individuality%20as%20well%20as%20his%20social%20being%20kept%20growing%20through%20later%20years.%20And%20in%201992%2C%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20his%2059th%20birthday%2C%20a%20group%20of%20litterateurs%20from%20Kerala%2C%20including%20renowned%20poets%20Sugatha%20Kumari%20and%20O.N.V%20Kurup%2C%20as%20well%20as%20some%20well%20wishers%20from%20the%20US%20gather%20around%20the%20Niagara%20waterfalls%20to%20celebrate%20it.%20In%20the%20same%20year%2C%20MT%20had%20yet%20another%20birthday%20celebration%20in%20the%20company%20of%20friends%20from%20the%20writers%E2%80%99%20and%20journalists%E2%80%99%20fraternity%2C%20at%20Stratford%20upon%20Avon%2C%20the%20birthplace%20of%20William%20Shakespeare.%20MT%20himself%20has%20fond%20memories%20of%20this%20celebration%20and%20some%20of%20his%20friends%20rate%20this%20as%20the%20best%20birthday%20the%20maestro%20has%20ever%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Sensibility%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20as%20NGK%20solemnly%20explained%20that%20day%2C%20MT%20had%20reached%20these%20heights%20combining%20his%20immense%20creativity%20and%20intense%20labour.%20This%20combination%20spanned%20diverse%20aspects%20of%20life%2C%20literature%20and%20arts.%20His%20literary%20output%20imparted%20a%20new%20sensibility%20to%20the%20Malayalam%20novel%20and%20the%20short%20story.%20This%20sensibility%20was%20evident%20in%20both%20form%20and%20content%20as%20well%20as%20the%20inexplicable%20beauty%20and%20rhythm%20of%20the%20language%20as%20reflected%20in%20literature.%20Along%20with%20fiction%2C%20he%20made%20forays%20into%20non-fiction%20commentary%20on%20contemporary%20issues%20and%20history.%20This%20too%20had%20his%20distinct%20stamp%20that%20captured%20the%20nuances%20of%20a%20given%20situation%20or%20the%20personalities%20involved%20in%20it%2C%20in%20a%20language%20and%20in%20a%20manner%20without%20parallel.%20In%20short%2C%20MT%E2%80%99s%20occupation%20with%20the%20written%20word%20added%20tremendous%20value%20to%20prose%20in%20the%20Malayalam%20language.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMany%20worlds%20of%20MT%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20MT%20became%20a%20much%20awarded%20film-maker%2C%20who%20once%20again%20pioneered%20and%20strengthened%20one%20particular%20stream%20of%20the%20neo-realist%20cinema%20in%20India.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20most%20illustrious%20literary%20editor%20that%20the%20journalism%20in%20Kerala%20has%20seen%20in%20its%20history.%20At%20least%20two%20generations%20of%20new%20writers%20owe%20their%20place%20in%20the%20limelight%20to%20this%20truly%20perceptive%20editor%2C%20whose%20journalistic%20endeavors%20not%20merely%20promoted%20Malayalam%20literature%E2%80%99s%20forays%20into%20modernism%20but%20literally%20galvanised%20it.%20Yet%20another%20attribute%20of%20MT%20is%20that%20he%20is%20an%20institution%20builder%2C%20particularly%20of%20cultural%20institutions%20that%20have%20proactively%20sought%20%E2%80%93%20with%20varying%20degrees%20of%20success%20%E2%80%93%20to%20rebuild%20the%20essence%20of%20the%20social%20and%20cultural%20trends%20often%20described%20as%20the%20Kerala%20Renaissance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151452%2FTHUNCHAN_MEMORIAL.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151452%2FTHUNCHAN_MEMORIAL.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16151452%2FTHUNCHAN_MEMORIAL-300x146.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663456%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22497%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThunchath%20Ezhuthachan%20Memorial.%20Photo%3A%20Vicharam%2FWikimedia%20commons%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20most%20important%20contribution%20in%20this%20regard%20is%20the%20Thunchath%20Ezhuthachan%20Memorial%2C%20at%20Tirur%20in%20north%20Kerala.%20Thunchath%20Ezhuthachan%2C%20considered%20the%20%E2%80%98father%20of%20Malayalam%20language%2C%20not%20only%20evolved%20the%2051-character%20alphabet%20system%20for%20the%20Malayalam%20equivalent%20of%20Sanskrit%2C%20but%20also%20made%20contributions%20to%20refine%20its%20style%20and%20imparted%20to%20it%20an%20%E2%80%98individuality%E2%80%99%20of%20its%20own.%20The%20collective%20effect%20of%20these%20diverse%20streams%20can%20only%20be%20termed%20as%20the%20MT%20phenomenon%2C%20which%20has%20held%20sway%20over%20successive%20generations%20of%20literary%20connoisseurs%2C%20cultural%20aesthetes%20and%20social%20observers%20in%20the%2020th%20and%2021st%20centuries.%20In%20chronological%20terms%2C%20this%20is%20an%20effect%20that%20has%20been%20conspicuous%20right%20through%20the%20nearly%20seven%20decades%20that%20Kerala%20has%20existed%20as%20a%20State%20in%20the%20sovereign%20republic%20of%20India.%20It%20is%20the%20emergence%20of%20this%20%E2%80%98MT%20phenomenon%E2%80%99%20that%20is%20at%20the%20root%20of%20the%20unique%20journeys%20of%20his%20birthday%20and%20the%20way%20its%20celebrations%20have%20evolved%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20three%20decades%20preceding%202023%20%E2%80%93%20that%20is%20his%2060th%20birthday%20%E2%80%93%20MT%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20is%20observed%20by%20Malayali%20communities%20across%20the%20world.%20Literary%20aficionados%20belonging%20to%20other%20communities%20and%20following%20other%20languages%20also%20become%20part%20of%20the%20celebrations.%20The%20media%20in%20Kerala%2C%20consisting%20of%20newspapers%2C%20portals%20and%20television%20in%20diverse%20languages%2C%20literally%20celebrates%20the%20birthday%20with%20some%20verve.%20Almost%20all%20newspapers%20have%20front-page%20coverages%20referring%20to%20the%20birthday%20and%20all%20other%20forms%20of%20media%2C%20including%20television%20and%20radio%2C%20have%20special%20packages%20of%20stories%20and%20commemorative%20features%20on%20various%20aspects%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20literary%2C%20social%20and%20personal%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%20these%20celebrations%20have%20touched%20a%20new%20high%2C%20especially%20because%20MT%20completes%20the%20auspicious%20%3Cem%3Enavathi%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0age%20of%2090.%20There%20are%20other%20reasons%20to%20celebrate%20too.%20The%20year%20also%20marks%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20internationally%20acclaimed%20pathbreaking%20neorealist%20Malayalam%20film%20%3Cem%3ENirmalyam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%2030th%20anniversary%20of%20his%20leadership%20of%20the%20Thunchan%20Memorial%20Trust.%20The%20different%20aspects%20of%20the%20MT%20phenomenon%20are%20also%20being%20celebrated%20through%20a%20series%20of%20events%20highlighting%20the%20landmark%20happenings%20in%20MT%E2%80%99s%20life.%20It%20started%20with%20a%20five-day%20festival%20at%20Thunchan%20Parambu%20titled%20S%3Cem%3Eaadaram%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Respectfully).%20The%20festival%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20chief%20minister%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%20on%20May%2016%20and%20the%20inaugural%20event%20was%20attended%20by%20film%20actor%20Mammotty.%20Over%20the%20five-day%20festival%2C%20different%20aspects%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20creative%20life%20%E2%80%93%20novel%2C%20short%20stories%2C%20cinema%2C%20journalism%2Ccultural%20interventions%20and%20institution%20building%20%E2%80%93%20were%20discussed%20from%20a%20historical%20and%20contemporary%20perspective.%20The%20discussion%20on%20MT%E2%80%99s%20novels%20generated%20a%20heated%20debate%20between%20Tamil%20writer%20Jayamohan%20and%20Malayalam%20critic%20M.M.%20Narayanan.%20Jayamohan%20analysed%20MT%E2%80%99s%20novels%20essentially%20as%20stories%20of%20individual%20alienation%20and%20pathos%20while%20Narayanan%20countered%20that%20these%20individual%20stories%20had%20deep%20historical%20and%20political%20dimensions%20too.%20The%20debate%20left%20its%20imprint%20on%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20social%20and%20cultural%20spaces%20for%20days%20on%20end%2C%20underscoring%20the%20continuing%20relevance%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20creative%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emotional%20aspect%20of%20the%20festival%20came%20out%20when%20renowned%20actors%20and%20directors%20of%20Malayalam%20cinema%20recalled%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20MT%20phenomenon%20on%20them.%20There%20was%20also%20a%20dance%20tribute%20to%20MT%20by%20his%20daughter%20and%20renowned%20Bharatnatyam%20danseuse%20Aswathy%20V%20Nair.%20The%20compositions%20were%20based%20on%20the%20songs%20that%20were%20part%20of%20the%20movies%20written%20and%2For%20directed%20by%20MT%20as%20well%20as%20his%20favorite%20verses%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3EMahabharata%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20Malayalam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98MT%4090%20celebrations%E2%80%99%20are%20continuing%20with%20different%20publications%20organising%20their%20own%20festivals.%20Mathrubhumi%2C%20the%20media%20house%20with%20considerable%20reach%20among%20Keralaites%20across%20the%20world%2C%20has%20begun%20its%20five%20day%20festival%20on%20July%2010%20at%20Kozhikode.%20It%20was%20inaugurated%20by%20celebrated%20filmmaker%20Maniratnam%20and%20attended%20by%20author%20Manu%20S.%20Pillai.%20%3Cem%3EMalayala%20Manorama%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20largest%20circulated%20Malayalam%20daily%2C%20has%20initiated%20celebrations%20lasting%2090%20days%20on%20July%2014.%20National%20and%20international%20celebrities%20from%20the%20world%20of%20literature%20and%20cinema%20are%20expected%20to%20participate%20in%20these%20celebrations%20to%20be%20held%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20top%20it%20all%2C%20the%20year%20would%20also%20witness%20the%20presentation%20of%20the%20movie%20productions%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20nine%20short%20stories%2C%20a%20majority%20of%20them%20directed%20by%20a%20clutch%20of%20celebrated%20directors.%20MT%E2%80%99s%20trip%20to%20the%20high%20ranges%20in%202022%20on%20his%2089th%20birthday%20was%20to%20witness%20shoots%20of%20one%20of%20these%20movies.%20Apart%20from%20Olavum%20Threeravum%2C%20Priyadarshan%20is%20directing%20%3Cem%3ESilalikhitham%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Inscriptions)%20too.%20MT%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20also%20makes%20her%20directorial%20debut%20in%20this%20series%20with%20%3Cem%3EVilpana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(The%20Sale).%20Other%20movies%20in%20the%20series%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20directors%20are%20as%20follows.%3Cem%3E%20Abhayam%20Thedi%20Veendum%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Once%20again%2C%20In%20Search%20of%20Refuge%2C%20Santosh%20Sivan%20)%2C%20%3Cem%3ESwargam%20Thurakkunna%20Samayam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(When%20the%20Doors%20of%20Heaven%20Open%2C%20Jayaraj%20)%2C%20%3Cem%3EKazhcha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Vision%2C%20Shyama%20Prasad)%2C%20%3Cem%3EKadalkkaattu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Sea%20Breeze%2C%20Rathish%20Ambat)%2C%20%3Cem%3ESherlock%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Mahesh%20Narayanan)%2C%20%3Cem%3EKadugannava%20Oru%20Yathra%20Kurippu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Kadugannava%2C%20A%20Travel%20Note%2C%20Ranjith).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20what%20is%20being%20celebrated%20across%20the%20Malayali%20universe%20is%20not%20MT%E2%80%99s%20actual%20birthday.%20July%2015%2C%20the%20date%20that%20is%20marked%20as%20MT%E2%80%99s%20birthday%20is%20one%20that%20was%20ascribed%20by%20an%20uncle%20of%20his%20while%20getting%20him%20admitted%20to%20an%20school%20before%20the%20permissible%20age%20of%20admission.%20In%20the%20initial%20years%20of%20his%20life%2Cthis%20oversight%20did%20not%20matter%20as%20there%20was%20no%20scope%20for%20birthday%20celebrations%20on%20account%20of%20colossal%20constraints%20of%20resources%20and%20social%20mobility.%20Later%2C%20the%20wrong%20date%20was%20widely%20acknowledged%20and%20honoured.%20Talking%20about%20this%20to%20me%2C%20MT%20had%20said%20at%20this%20later%20stage%20too%2C%20there%20was%20no%20urge%20to%20correct%20the%20mistake%2C%20because%20signifying%20birthdays%20was%20not%20a%20primary%20concern%20for%20him.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20he%20indicated%20that%20his%20was%20an%20approach%20that%20sought%20to%20paraphrase%20Shakespeare%E2%80%99s%20famous%20quote%20%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20in%20a%20name%3F%20That%20which%20we%20call%20a%20rose%2FBy%20any%20other%20name%20would%20smell%20as%20sweet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20put%20the%20record%20straight%2C%20MT%E2%80%99s%20real%20date%20of%20birth%20is%20not%20July%2015%2C%20but%20August%209.%20A%20majority%20of%20those%20who%20have%20sought%20to%20chronicle%20parts%20of%20MT%E2%80%99s%20life%20with%20some%20precision%20have%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20Gregorian%20calendar%20was%20not%20followed%20in%20MT%E2%80%99s%20ancestral%20home.%20The%20norm%20was%20to%20follow%20the%20Malayalam%20%E2%80%9CKolla%20Varsham%20%E2%80%9Ccalendar.%20As%20per%20this%20calendar%2C%20MT%20was%20born%20on%20Uthrattathi%20day%20in%20Karkitakam%20in%20the%20Kolla%20Varsham%201108.%20This%20was%20the%2025th%20day%20of%20Karkitakam%20that%20year.%20MT%20says%20that%2C%20in%20the%20early%20years%20of%20his%20life%20no%20one%20really%20cross%20checked%20the%20corresponding%20date%20on%20the%20Gregorian%20calendar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20cross-checking%20was%20done%20decades%20later%2C%20around%20the%20mid-1960s%2C%20after%20MT%20had%20become%20a%20celebrated%20Malayalam%20writer.%20Even%20when%20the%20cross-checking%20was%20done%2C%20the%20unique%20methods%20of%20calculation%20of%20days%20and%20months%20in%20the%20Kolla%20Varsham%20calendar%20created%20their%20own%20quirky%20results.%20Thus%2C%20the%20corresponding%20date%20in%20the%20Gregorian%20calendar%20was%20shown%20as%20August%208%20as%20per%20some%20calculations%20and%20as%20August%209%20in%20some%20others.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20serious%20effort%20to%20rationalise%20the%20different%20dates%2C%20in%20all%20probability%2C%20following%20the%20paraphrased%20Shakespearean%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%E2%80%99s%20in%20a%20date%E2%80%9D%20logic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20same%2C%20since%20the%20date%2015th%20of%20July%20was%20entered%20in%20application%20forms%20while%20getting%20admitted%20to%20school%20as%20a%20kid%2C%20the%20date%20has%20got%20stuck.%20Not%20just%20in%20official%20records%2C%20but%20in%20the%20collective%20social%20memory%20of%20Keralites%20as%20a%20whole.%20And%20year%20after%20year%2C%20the%20media%20celebrates%20this%20collective%20consciousness.%20July%202023%20is%20no%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheaidem.com%2Fmt-vasudevan-nair-child-of-karkitakam%2F%5C%22%3Eoriginally%20published%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20The%20AIDEM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689501983000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16150754%2F1280px-M_T_Vasudevan_Nair.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fcelebrating-keralas-renaissance-man-m-t-vasudevan-nair%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20two%20generations%20of%20new%20writers%20owe%20their%20place%20in%20the%20limelight%20to%20this%20truly%20perceptive%20editor%2C%20whose%20journalistic%20endeavors%20not%20merely%20promoted%20Malayalam%20literature%E2%80%99s%20forays%20into%20modernism%20but%20literally%20galvanised%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fcelebrating-keralas-renaissance-man-m-t-vasudevan-nair%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Net%20debt%20of%20top%208%20listed%20realty%20firms%20dip%2043%25%20in%20last%203%20years%3A%20Anarock%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689501011000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-12%2F22%2Ffull%2F1671682054-7138.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fnet-debt-of-top-8-listed-realty-firms-dip-43-in-last-3-years-anarock-123071600337_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20average%20cost%20of%20debt%20for%20these%20eight%20players%20fell%20to%209%25%20in%20FY23%20from%2010.3%25%20in%20FY20.%20In%202020-21%2C%20the%20interest%20cost%20was%209.05%25%2C%20while%20the%20cost%20of%20debt%20was%207.96%25%20in%202021-22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fnet-debt-of-top-8-listed-realty-firms-dip-43-in-last-3-years-anarock-123071600337_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fnet-debt-of-top-8-listed-realty-firms-dip-43-in-last-3-years-anarock-123071600337_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fnet-debt-of-top-8-listed-realty-firms-dip-43-in-last-3-years-anarock-123071600337_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Is%20France%20So%20Eager%20to%20Cosy%20Up%20to%20an%20Authoritarian%20Narendra%20Modi%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16150816%2FF1BDWMXaAAAcB-i.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3EI%3C%2Fspan%3Endia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20economic%20relationship%20with%20France%20is%20different%20from%20other%20comparable%20countries%20in%20one%20key%20area%3A%20their%20bilateral%20trade%20in%20goods.%20While%20Germany%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20recorded%20significant%20volumes%20%E2%80%93%20%2425bn%20and%20%2417bn%20respectively%20last%20year%20%E2%80%93%20France%E2%80%99s%20total%2C%20excluding%20military%20sales%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.india-briefing.com%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20just%20over%20%2412bn%3C%2Fa%3E.%20French%20businesses%20are%20less%20well%20established%20in%20India%20than%20those%20from%20other%20European%20countries%2C%20with%20a%20few%20high-profile%20exceptions%20such%20as%20Capgemini%2C%20a%20technology%20services%20and%20consulting%20firm%2C%20half%20of%20whose%20350%2C000%20workers%20are%20employed%20there.%20But%20France%20ranks%2011th%20among%20foreign%20investors%20in%20India%2C%20while%20the%20Netherlands%20is%20fourth%2C%20and%20Germany%2C%20a%20commercial%20power%20first%20and%20foremost%2C%20comes%20ninth%2C%20with%20200%20Indian%20investors%20active%20in%20Germany.%20Likewise%2C%20despite%20efforts%20by%20the%20French%20authorities%20and%20academics%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Indian%20students%20on%20French%20campuses%20%E2%80%93%20around%20ten%20thousand%20%E2%80%93%20lags%20far%20behind%20Germany%2C%20which%20had%2034%2C000%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driving%20force%20of%20Franco-Indian%20relations%20is%20elsewhere%2C%20in%20the%20sovereign%20realm%20of%20strategy%2C%20and%20indeed%20security%2C%20where%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20role%20is%20greater%20than%20in%20the%20economy.%20Both%20countries%20justify%20their%20closeness%20as%20being%20in%20their%20national%20interest%2C%20invoking%20the%20%E2%80%98democratic%20values%E2%80%99%20they%20supposedly%20share.%20Yet%20India%E2%80%99s%20recent%20political%20evolution%20completely%20undermines%20this.%20So%20where%20do%20France%E2%80%99s%20short-%20and%20long-term%20interests%20really%20lie%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrance%E2%80%99s%20Indo-Pacific%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGeopolitically%2C%20India%20has%20long%20been%20France%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20partner%20%E2%80%93%20officially%20since%20January%201998%2C%20when%20Jacques%20Chirac%20made%20a%20historic%20presidential%20visit%20at%20a%20time%20when%20India%20lacked%20a%20stable%20government%20and%20was%20just%20weeks%20from%20the%20election%20that%20brought%20to%20power%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20the%20first%20Hindu%20nationalist%20prime%20minister%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20Soon%20after%2C%20his%20government%E2%80%99s%20nuclear%20tests%20were%20widely%20condemned%20by%20the%20international%20community%20(India%20has%20never%20signed%20the%20Non-Proliferation%20Treaty)%2C%20but%20not%20by%20France.%20The%20US%2C%20Japan%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20UK%20and%20many%20other%20countries%20imposed%20sanctions%2C%20but%20France%20showed%20an%20indulgence%20that%20India%20still%20remembers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20current%20context%2C%20this%2025-year-old%20strategic%20partnership%20has%20taken%20on%20increased%20importance%20because%20of%20China%E2%80%99s%20rise%2C%20particularly%20as%20manifested%20by%20a%20new%20kind%20of%20influence%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean.%20Countries%20in%20the%20region%2C%20such%20as%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20which%20have%20taken%20on%20loans%20from%20Chinese%20lenders%20for%20large-scale%20projects%2C%20now%20find%20their%20sovereignty%20weakened.%20France%2C%20as%20a%20resident%20power%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20where%20much%20of%20its%20exclusive%20economic%20zone%20(EEZ)%20is%20located%20because%20of%20its%20overseas%20territories%2C%20is%20concerned%20about%20this%20expansionism.%20So%20is%20New%20Delhi%2C%20to%20an%20even%20greater%20extent%2C%20as%20it%20is%20beginning%20to%20feel%20encircled%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20Chinese%20presence%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Nepal%20and%20Bangladesh.%20These%20mutual%20interests%20in%20the%20region%20partly%20explain%20India%E2%80%99s%20place%20in%20France%E2%80%99s%20Indo-Pacific%20strategy%2C%20first%20presented%20by%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20in%20May%202018%20in%20a%20speech%20in%20Sydney%2C%20in%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmondediplo.com%2F2021%2F06%2F08bulard%5C%22%3Ehe%20described%20China%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20in%20the%20region%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98gamechanger%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20official%20statements%20on%20the%20subject%20present%20India%20as%20France%E2%80%99s%20key%20partner%20in%20the%20region%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20trilateral%20dialogues%20that%20France%20and%20India%20have%20had%20with%20Australia%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20(UAE).%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Indian%20government%20has%20helped%20Paris%20gain%20membership%20to%20multilateral%20(or%20%E2%80%98minilateral%E2%80%99)%20bodies%20on%20account%20of%20its%20extensive%20maritime%20footprint%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Rim%20Association%20(IORA)%2C%20which%20it%20joined%20in%202020.%20This%20has%20resulted%20in%20bilateral%20military%20manoeuvres%2C%20the%20earliest%20of%20which%2C%20Varuna%2C%20has%20been%20an%20annual%20event%20since%202001%3B%20the%20aircraft%20carrier%20Cl%C3%A9menceau%20took%20part%20in%20it%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20position%20of%20the%20French%20government%2C%20which%20regards%20India%20as%20its%20preferred%20partner%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20particularly%20to%20resist%20China%E2%80%99s%20inroads%2C%20is%20worth%20examining.%20Academic%20Ashley%20Tellis%20is%20one%20of%20those%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foreignaffairs.com%2Findia%2Famericas-bad-bet-india-modi%5C%22%3Einitiated%20this%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%99%20relations%20with%20India.%20He%20has%20argued%20that%20Washington%2C%20where%20Narendra%20Modi%20made%20a%20state%20visit%20in%20June%2C%20%E2%80%98has%20made%20an%20enormous%20bet%E2%80%99%20on%20India%2C%20treating%20it%20as%20a%20key%20partner%20simply%20because%20the%20US%20has%20neither%20the%20means%20nor%20inclination%20to%20confront%20Beijing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20view%20is%20supported%20by%20three%20facts.%20First%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20is%20much%20weaker%20than%20China%E2%80%99s%2C%20its%20largest%20trading%20partner%2C%20on%20which%20it%20is%20heavily%20reliant.%20Second%2C%20New%20Delhi%20prefers%20not%20to%20react%20to%20China%E2%80%99s%20territorial%20encroachment%20in%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20which%20is%20visible%20in%20satellite%20images%2C%20to%20avoid%20initiating%20hostilities%20in%20which%20India%20would%20come%20off%20worse.%20Third%2C%20India%20and%20China%20continue%20to%20collaborate%20within%20BRICS%20(Brazil%2C%20Russia%2C%20India%2C%20China%2C%20South%20Africa)%20to%20dislodge%20Western%20powers%20from%20their%20positions%20of%20power%20in%20the%20UN%20system%2C%20mainly%20because%20both%20reject%20the%20West%E2%80%99s%20vision%20of%20the%20liberal%20international%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20read%20the%20rest%20of%20this%20article%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmondediplo.com%2F2023%2F07%2F14india-france%5C%22%3ELe%20Monde%20diplomatique%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20first%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmondediplo.com%2F%5C%22%3EEnglish%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.monde-diplomatique.fr%2F%5C%22%3EFrench%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%20Le%20Monde%20diplomatique.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EChristophe%20Jaffrelot%20is%20a%20senior%20research%20fellow%20at%20CERI-Sciences%20Po%2FCNRS%2C%20Paris%2C%20Professor%20of%20Indian%20Politics%20and%20Sociology%20at%20King%E2%80%99s%20India%20Institute%2C%20London%2C%20and%20non-resident%20scholar%20at%20the%20Carnegie%20Endowment%20for%20International%20Peace.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689500353000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16150816%2FF1BDWMXaAAAcB-i.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Ffrance-emmanuel-macron-narendra-modi-strategy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20driving%20force%20of%20Franco-Ind