ia%2Fajit-pawar-other-maha-ncp-ministers-meet-sharad-pawar-in-mumbai%2Farticleshow%2F101798799.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20surprise%20move%2C%20Maharashtra%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20along%20with%20Praful%20Patel%2C%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%20and%20some%20other%20ministers%20from%20his%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20camp%20met%20NCP%20president%20Sharad%20Pawar%20at%20Mumbai's%20YB%20Chavan%20Centre%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fajit-pawar-other-maha-ncp-ministers-meet-sharad-pawar-in-mumbai%2Farticleshow%2F101798799.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Narendra%20Modi%20Knows%20an%20Actual%20UCC%20Will%20Be%20an%20Electoral%20Disaster%20for%20Him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F09092822%2FIMG_1682.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20all%20cousins%20be%20allowed%20to%20marry%2C%20or%20nieces%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fstate%2Fsc-declines-to-recognise-marriage-with-maternal-uncle-776627.html%5C%22%3Ematernal%20uncles%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Or%20will%20that%20be%20banned%20for%20all%20in%20the%20new%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%2C%20including%20those%20communities%20currently%20exempted%20from%20the%20Hindu%20Marriage%20Act%E2%80%99s%20ban%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fedit-page%2Fa-question-of-balance%2Farticleshow%2F5941357.cms%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98sapinda%E2%80%99%20marriages%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Will%20we%20all%20have%20to%20follow%20Christian%20family%20law%20when%20we%20wish%20to%20divorce%3F%20Will%20rules%20from%20the%20Muslim%20personal%20code%20apply%20as%20regards%20inheritance%20and%20sharing%20of%20property%20with%20parents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1051903%2Fagnates-cognates-half-bloods-and-full-bloods-the-real-challenge-in-drafting-a-uniform-civil-code%5C%22%3Eif%20one%20dies%20intestate%20or%20perhaps%2C%20Parsi%20rules%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20Will%20everyone%20be%20allowed%20to%20avail%20of%20the%20attractive%20tax%20benefits%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Undivided%20Family%20(HUF)%3F%20Or%20will%20that%20be%20abolished%20for%20all%2C%20uniformly%3F%20Will%20all%20Indians%20be%20forced%20to%20follow%20Santhal%20customs%3F%20Or%20Naga%20ones%3F%20(By%20the%20way%2C%20even%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiacode.nic.in%2Fshow-data%3Factid%3DAC_CEN_5_23_000010_197402_1517807320555%26orderno%3D1%5C%22%3ECode%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%2C%201973%20does%20not%20apply%20to%20Nagaland%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENothing%20is%20known%20as%20there%20is%20no%20publicly%20available%20draft%20of%20a%20UCC%20being%20talked%20up%20by%20the%20BJP.%20What%20we%20know%20is%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20dislikes%20diversity%20and%20sees%20diverse%20practices%20as%20a%20threat%20to%20the%20Indian%20Union.%20It%20said%20so%20in%20its%20affidavit%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20October%202022%2C%20in%20response%20to%20a%20petition%20on%20the%20UCC.%20The%20Union%20government%20said%20that%20citizens%20belonging%20to%20different%20religions%20and%20denominations%20adhering%20to%20different%20property%20and%20matrimonial%20laws%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcentre-files-affidavit-on-uniform-civil-code-in-sc-says-different-religions-following-different-laws-affronting-national-unity%2Farticle66026485.ece%5C%22%3Ean%20%E2%80%9Caffront%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20unity%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20last%20month%20too%20referred%20to%20%E2%80%9Cseparate%20laws%20for%20separate%20communities%E2%80%9D%20and%20said%20that%20the%20country%20could%20not%20run%20on%20a%20dual%20system.%20Oddly%2C%20this%20was%20not%20in%20some%20meeting%20or%20address%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20but%20while%20addressing%20booth-level%20workers%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20Bhopal.%20It%20is%20clearly%20in%20an%20electoral%20context%20that%20the%20UCC%20is%20being%20referred%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20is%20where%20the%20catch%20is.%20The%20BJP%20may%20be%20picking%20on%20an%20electorally%20indigestible%20bone.%20The%20fact%20is%20that%20attempts%20to%20suddenly%20spring%20a%20UCC%20on%20all%20Hindus%20too%20would%20be%20a%20disaster.%20Maybe%20that%20is%20why%20there%20is%20no%20draft.%20In%20Uttarakhand%2C%20for%20example%2C%20where%20a%20committee%20has%20been%20constituted%20by%20the%20BJP%20state%20government%20under%20Justice%20(retd)%20Ranjana%20Desai%2C%20to%20work%20one%20out%20for%20the%20state%2C%20there%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbehind-uttarakhand-ucc-13-months-of-consultations-38-public-meetings-8697983%2F%5C%22%3E13%20months%20of%20consultations%2C%2038%20public%20meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20no%20report%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20emphasis%20is%20on%20uniformity%20and%20not%20progressive%20or%20better%20or%20emancipatory.%20So%2C%20what%20or%20whose%20laws%20will%20be%20imposed%20on%20the%20whole%20nation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDirective%20or%20p%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Erinciple%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Article%2044%20of%20the%20Constitution%20%E2%80%93%20contained%20in%20Part%20IV%2C%20i.e.%20the%20Directive%20Principles%20of%20State%20Policy%20%E2%80%93%20speaks%20of%20a%20UCC%2C%20it%20is%20non-justiciable%20and%20just%20an%20ideal%20objective.%20The%20Directive%20Principles%20(Article%2036%20to%2051)%20are%20violated%20with%20impunity%20and%20often%20by%20the%20state%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%20Consider%20just%20Article%2043A%2C%20on%20the%20same%20page%20as%20the%20UCC%2C%20which%20reads%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20shall%20take%20steps%2C%20by%20suitable%20legislation%20or%20in%20any%20other%20way%2C%20to%20secure%20the%20participation%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20management%20of%20undertakings%2C%20establishments%20or%20other%20organisations%20engaged%20in%20any%20industry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20back%20to%20Article%2044%2C%20Dr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20had%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fambedkar-favoured-common-civil-code%2Farticle7934565.ece%5C%22%3Ein%20November%201948%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20envisaged%20a%20way%20around%20it%3A%20that%20a%20voluntary%20offer%20may%20be%20the%20way%20of%20bringing%20a%20consensus%20on%20such%20wide-ranging%20practices%3B%20%E2%80%9Ca%20provision%20by%20way%20of%20making%20a%20beginning%20that%20the%20Code%20shall%20apply%20only%20to%20those%20who%20make%20a%20declaration%20that%20they%20are%20prepared%20to%20be%20bound%20by%20it%2C%20so%20that%20in%20the%20initial%20stage%20the%20application%20of%20the%20Code%20may%20be%20purely%20voluntary%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%20so%20that%20the%20fear%20which%20my%20friends%20have%20expressed%20here%20will%20be%20altogether%20nullified.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22BJP's%20Clamour%20for%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20Driven%20by%20Aim%20of%20Dividing%2C%20Not%20Uniting%2C%20Indians%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjps-clamour-for-uniform-civil-code-driven-by-aim-of-dividing-not-uniting-indians%5C%22%3EBJP%E2%80%99s%20Clamour%20for%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20Driven%20by%20Aim%20of%20Dividing%2C%20Not%20Uniting%2C%20Indians%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20there%20already%20is%20a%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%201954%2C%20providing%20a%20legal%20umbrella%20for%20inter-religious%2C%20inter-caste%20marriages.%20In%3Cem%3E%20The%20Intimate%20State%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Perveez%20Mody%20has%20studied%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprotections%20(and%20obstructions)%20presented%20by%20the%20law%20to%20those%20who%20transform%20their%20new%20forms%20of%20intimacy%20into%20marriage%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%9D.%20A%20true%20progressive%20approach%20would%20be%20to%20expand%20the%20legal%20limits%20of%20how%20%E2%80%98relations%20of%20intimacy%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20%E2%80%98family%E2%80%99%20are%20thought%20of%2C%20ideally%20to%20break%20caste%20endogamy%20and%20perhaps%20even%20annihilate%20caste.%20India%20needs%20a%20civil%20code%20that%20is%20uniformly%20progressive%2C%20rather%20than%20uniformly%20regressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20target%20may%20be%20Muslim%20but%20enough%20groups%20which%20are%20parts%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20calculus%20%E2%80%93%20i.e.%20tribals%2C%20Goans%2C%20people%20in%20the%20north-eastern%20states%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Parsis%20and%20Christians%20%E2%80%93%20have%20made%20their%20case%20and%20already%20want%20out%20of%20an%20unknown%20uniformity%20being%20sought%20to%20be%20imposed.%20This%20opposition%20will%20spell%20disaster%20for%20the%20BJP%20if%20it%20pursues%20the%20matter%20in%20an%20election%20year.%20Maybe%20that%20explains%20the%20chronology%20of%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20having%20assured%20a%2012-member%20Nagaland%20government%20delegation%2C%20led%20by%20chief%20minister%20Neiphiu%20Rio%2C%20that%20the%20government%20is%20considering%20exempting%20Christians%20and%20some%20pockets%20of%20tribal%20areas%20from%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20proposed%20contentious%20UCC.%20The%20state%20government%20of%20Nagaland%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmorungexpress.com%2Fcentre-considering-exemption-of-christians-tribal-areas-from-ucc-purview-state-govt%5C%22%3Eactually%20said%20so%20in%20an%20official%20press%20release%20on%20July%207%3C%2Fa%3E.%20So%2C%20Schedule%20Six%2C%20the%20box%20for%20exceptions%20is%20already%20being%20carved%20up.%20Article%20371%20(A%20to%20J)%20mandates%20exceptions%20for%20regions%20and%20persons.%20So%2C%20once%20it%20is%20decided%20that%20there%20is%20a%20%E2%80%98uniform%E2%80%99%2C%20who%20will%20be%20exempted%20and%20who%20won%E2%80%99t%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMechanics%20of%20it%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Law%20Commission%20is%20being%20relied%20upon%20as%20the%20nodal%20body%20to%20work%20on%20the%20UCC%20to%20prepare%20something%20the%20BJP%20wants.%20But%20the%20Law%20Commission%20has%20already%20said%20clearly%20in%20para%201.15%20of%20a%20detailed%20report%20in%202018%20that%20a%20UCC%20was%20%E2%80%9Cneither%20necessary%20nor%20desirable%E2%80%9D.%20To%20cite%20the%20full%20sentence%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20Commission%20has%20therefore%20dealt%20with%20laws%20that%20are%20discriminatory%20rather%20than%20providing%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20which%20is%20neither%20necessary%20nor%20desirable%20at%20this%20stage.%20Most%20countries%20are%20now%20moving%20towards%20recognition%20of%20difference%2C%20and%20the%20mere%20existence%20of%20difference%20does%20not%20imply%20discrimination%2C%20but%20is%20indicative%20of%20a%20robust%20democracy.%E2%80%9D%20That%20is%20completely%20at%20variance%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98one%20size%20fits%20all%E2%80%99%20being%20sought%20by%20a%20majoritarian%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20the%20BJP%20government%20cares%20for%20the%20sanctity%20of%20the%20Law%20Commission%20is%20clear%20from%20at%20least%20two%20facts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20it%20is%20disregarding%20the%20recommendations%20of%20its%20own%20appointees%20in%20the%2021st%20Law%20Commission%20from%202018%20saying%20the%20UCC%20is%20a%20no%20go%20and%20personal%20laws%20should%20just%20be%20urged%20to%20evolve%20out%20of%20bad%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecondly%2C%20this%20government%20did%20not%20bother%20to%20appoint%20members%20to%20the%2022nd%C2%A0Law%20Commission%20for%20years.%20The%2022%3Csup%3End%3C%2Fsup%3E%20Law%20Commission%20was%20a%20ghost%20commission%20for%20nearly%20all%20of%20its%20three-year%20term.%20Notified%20on%20February%2021%2C%202020%2C%20it%20was%20kept%20vacant%20for%20two%20years%20and%20nine%20months%20of%20its%20three-year%20term.%20A%20chairperson%2C%20Justice%C2%A0Rituraj%20Awasthi%C2%A0(retd)%2C%20finally%20assumed%20office%20on%C2%A0November%209%2C%202022.%20Its%20term%20has%20now%20been%20extended%20till%20August%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%2021st%20Law%20Commission%20put%20forth%20its%20questionnaire%20in%20the%20public%20domain%20in%20November%202016%2C%20it%20received%20over%2075%2C378%20responses.%20This%20time%2C%20the%2022nd%C2%A0Law%20Commission%20has%20to%20deal%20with%2046%20lakh%20responses.%20What%20is%20the%20process%20for%20sifting%20through%20this%3F%20What%20is%20the%20process%20of%20reinventing%20the%20UCC%20wheel%3F%20Nothing%20is%20known.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProgressive%20civil%20code%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20a%20citizen%E2%80%99s%20group%20comprising%20activist%20Bezwada%20Wilson%2C%20lawyer%20Dushyant%2C%20actor%20Gul%20Panag%2C%20academic%20and%20author%20Mukul%20Kesavan%2C%20author%20Nilanjana%20Roy%2C%20scholar%20S.%20Irfan%20Habib%2C%20Major%20General%20S.%20Vombetkere%20(retd)%20and%20musician%20T.M.%20Krishna%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.thewire.in%2Farticle%2Fgovernment%2Funiform-civil-code-draft-law-commission%2Famp%5C%22%3Epresented%20a%20proposal%20of%20a%20model%20progressive%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Justice%20B.S.%20Chauhan%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Law%20Commission.%20They%20conceived%20of%20the%20abolition%20of%20the%20HUF%2C%20gender-neutral%20marriage%20and%20inheritance%20laws%2C%20which%20would%20entitle%20all%20children%20%E2%80%93%20biological%2C%20adopted%2C%20surrogate%2C%20%E2%80%98legitimate%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98illegitimate%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20to%20inherit%20property.%20In%20a%20supporting%20letter%2C%20former%20attorney%20general%20Soli%20J.%20Sorabjee%2C%20who%20forwarded%20the%20draft%20code%20to%20Justice%20Chauhan%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20join%20those%20who%20wish%20to%20ensure%20that%20any%20step%20ahead%20to%20bring%20everyone%20on%20the%20same%20page%20must%20be%20progressive%20and%20enlightened.%E2%80%9D%20Sorabjee%20added%20that%20the%20Law%20Commissions%20recommendations%20on%20a%20UCC%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9Cfar-sighted%20and%20progressive%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20root%20of%20the%20problem%20is%20how%20Modi%20and%20his%20government%20view%20diversity.%20A%20good%20talking%20point%20for%20foreign%20trips%2C%20it%20came%20up%20in%20Paris%20too%20on%20Thursday.%20But%20it%20is%20an%20%E2%80%9Caffront%20to%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20unity%E2%80%9D%20for%20domestic%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20the%20many%20species%20of%20flora%20and%20fauna%20in%20the%20Amazon%20forest%2C%20the%20diversity%20of%20India%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Efact%3C%2Fem%3E.%20But%20inclusiveness%20or%20wanting%20a%20healthy%20and%20plural%20pastiche%20is%20an%20%3Cem%3Eact%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20speaks%20to%20what%20a%20society%20wants%20to%20do%20with%20its%20diversity.%20As%20a%20modern%20democracy%20in%201950%2C%20India%20was%20anxious%20to%20embrace%20it.%20The%20same%20cannot%20be%20said%20for%20India%2075%20years%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22BJP%20Equates%20UCC%20With%20Gender%20Justice.%20But%20Can%20It%20End%20Discrimination%20In-Built%20in%20Personal%20Laws%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fbjp-ucc-with-gender-justice-discrimination-personal-laws%5C%22%3EBJP%20Equates%20UCC%20With%20Gender%20Justice.%20But%20Can%20It%20End%20Discrimination%20In-Built%20in%20Personal%20Laws%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20wanting%20a%20UCC%20is%20the%20obsession%20with%20the%20%E2%80%98U%E2%80%99.%202023%20calls%20for%20a%20Progressive%20or%20a%20P%2C%20a%20PCC.%20But%20a%20majoritarian%20BJP%20is%20keen%20on%20just%20clinging%20onto%20anything%20it%20hopes%20will%20fire%20its%20base.%20It%20is%20evident%20that%20the%20purpose%20is%20to%20indulge%20in%20performative%20exclusion%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20to%20tell%20its%20base%20that%20it%20has%20obliterated%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20would%20also%20like%20to%20say%20it%20has%20been%20able%20to%20impose%20the%20%E2%80%98uniformity%E2%80%99%20of%20Hindu%20Law%20but%20there%20is%20no%20one%20Hindu%20law%20which%20will%20be%20acceptable%20across%20the%20country%20to%20all%20Hindus%20and%20non-Hindus%20(i.e.%2C%20not%20just%20Muslims%20but%20Christians%2C%20Parsis%2C%20Tribals%2C%20Sikhs%20etc.)%20Any%20exercise%20that%20dives%20into%20the%20details%2C%20even%20if%20a%20stitched-up%20quickie%20Code%2C%20will%20be%20a%20Pandora%E2%80%99s%20box%2C%20full%20of%20elements%20unacceptable%20to%20everyone%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%20the%20UCC%20as%20a%20concrete%20proposal%20is%20AWOL.%20Try%20persuading%20any%20Hindu%20family%20in%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20constituency%20in%20UP%20that%20it%20is%20ok%20to%20marry%20a%20%3Cem%3Emama%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20first-cousin.%20And%20try%20persuading%20a%20Hindu%20family%20in%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%E2%80%99s%20home%20state%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20to%20stop%20doing%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689497235000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F09092822%2FIMG_1682.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-knows-an-actual-ucc-will-be-an-electoral-disaster-for-him%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Who%20will%20it%20be%20uniform%20for%3F%20The%20chronology%20is%20clear%20as%20Hindus%20would%20want%20out%20too.%20The%20BJP%20realises%20this%20and%20hence%2C%20there%20is%20no%20UCC%20draft%20being%20made%20available%2C%20just%20hot%20air.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-knows-an-actual-ucc-will-be-an-electoral-disaster-for-him%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20ordinance%3A%20Cong%20won't%20support%3B%20AAP%20calls%20it%2