0secretary%20in%20charge%20of%20communications%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20in%20Bengaluru%20is%20expected%20to%20bring%20together%20leaders%20from%2024%20non-BJP%20parties%2C%20providing%20a%20platform%20to%20strategize%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20join%20the%20gathering%20this%20time%2C%20which%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20expand%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20that%20currently%20consists%20of%20around%20150%20Lok%20Sabha%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689495480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fgb11k1sg_opposition-meet-ani-650_650x400_23_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-arent-going-to-support-it-congresss-kc-venugopal-on-centres-delhi-ordinance-day-before-big-opposition-meet-4211966%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20marathon%20outreach%20by%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20boss%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20nearly%20all%20opposition%20parties%2C%20except%20the%20Congress%2C%20had%20pledged%20to%20help%20his%20party%20block%20the%20move%20in%20the%20upper%20house%20of%20parliament.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-arent-going-to-support-it-congresss-kc-venugopal-on-centres-delhi-ordinance-day-before-big-opposition-meet-4211966%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-arent-going-to-support-it-congresss-kc-venugopal-on-centres-delhi-ordinance-day-before-big-opposition-meet-4211966%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwe-arent-going-to-support-it-congresss-kc-venugopal-on-centres-delhi-ordinance-day-before-big-opposition-meet-4211966%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Had%20No%20Clue%20Who%20Yuzi%20Chahal%20Was%5C%22%3A%20Wife%20Dhanashree%20Makes%20Candid%20Confession%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20cricketer%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yuzvendra%20Chahal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1394-yuzvendra-chahal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYuzvendra%20Chahal%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20primarily%20known%20for%20his%20ability%20to%20deceive%20batters%20with%20his%20spin%20bowling.%20But%2C%20away%20from%20the%20field%2C%20the%20leg-spinner%20also%20managed%20to%20win%20over%20the%20hearts%20of%20Dhanashree%20Verma%2C%20now%20his%20wife.%20In%20a%20never-heard-before%20revelation%2C%20both%20Chahal%20and%20his%20Dhanashree%20opened%20up%20on%20their%20journey%2C%20starting%20from%20how%20they%20got%20to%20know%20each%20other%20to%20eventually%20deciding%20to%20tie%20the%20knot.%20During%20an%20interview%2C%20Dhanashree%20even%20revealed%20that%20she%20didn't%20even%20know%20that%20Chahal%20was%20an%20Indian%20cricketer%20when%20the%20two%20met%20for%20the%20first%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20chat%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dqr8R0cf2rq0%26t%3D152s%5C%22%3EThe%20Ranveer%20Show%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Chahal%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20first%20sent%20a%20message%20to%20Dhanashree%20as%20he%20wanted%20to%20learn%20dance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20Had%20DMd%20her%2C%20having%20seen%20her%20dance%20on%20TikTok%20and%20a%20number%20of%20other%20reels.%20I%20asked%20her%20if%20gives%20classes%20as%20I%20had%20nothing%20to%20do%20in%20Lockdown.%20I%20wanted%20to%20learn%20something%20new.%20Once%20I%20messaged%20her%2C%20we%20started%20with%20online%20classes.%20First%20two%20months%2C%20we%20didn't%20talk%20about%20anything%20else%20but%20dance.%20I%20didn't%20flirt%20at%20all.%20We%20are%20not%20even%20friends%2C%20only%20had%20dance-related%20talks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20India%20spinner%20even%20said%20that%20he%20was%20impressed%20by%20how%20lively%20Dhanashree%20was%20even%20during%20the%20miserable%20times%20of%20Covid%20lockdown.%20Having%20been%20impressed%20by%20her%20vibes%2C%20Chahal%20then%20decided%20to%20pop%20the%20question%20and%20asked%20her%20to%20marry%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20asked%20her%20how%20are%20you%20so%20happy%2C%20even%20during%20this%20phase%20of%20lockdown.%20Then%20she%20started%20to%20talk%20about%20her%20life.%20That%20is%20where%20our%20conversations%20started.%20I%20liked%20her%20vibes.%20She%20is%20a%20self-made%20woman%20like%20I%20am%20a%20self-made%20man.%20I%20told%20my%20mom%20about%20her%2C%20that%20I%20like%20this%20girl.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20I%20told%20her%20(Dhanashree)%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20date%20you%2C%20I%20want%20to%20marry%20you.%20I%20said%20that%20straight%20away.%20I%20was%20sure.%20We%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20chats%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20revealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Dhanashree%20was%20asked%20about%20her%20impression%20of%20Chahal%2C%20she%20revealed%20that%20was%20a%20really%20passionate%20student%20who%20would%20work%20hard%20on%20whatever%20homework%20was%20given%20to%20him.%20She%20revealed%20that%20it%20was%20Chahal's%20decency%20and%20directness%20is%20that%20impressed%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20always%20liked%20people%20who%20are%20passionate%20about%20their%20passion.%20I%20used%20to%20watch%20cricket%20for%20a%20long%20time%20but%20when%20I%20stopped%20watching%20cricket%2C%20he%20made%20his%20India%20debut.%20I%20think%2C%20that%20is%20a%20really%20good%20thing.%20When%20he%20messaged%20me%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20take%20dance%20classes%2C%20I%20had%20no%20clue%20who%20Yuzi%20Chahal%20was.%20He%20was%20very%20sincere%20about%20dance%20and%20I%20liked%20it.%20Whenever%20I%20would%20give%20him%20homework%2C%20he%20would%20practice%20too.%20He%20used%20to%20send%20videos%2C%20asking%20where%20he%20can%20do%20good.%20This%20is%20why%20the%20classes%20lasted%20for%202%20months.%20Decency%20is%20what%20I%20loved%20about%20him.%20The%20way%2C%20as%20a%20student%20who%20he%20was%20with%20him%2C%20as%20a%20friend%20who%20he%20was%20with%20me%2C%20and%20the%20direct%20approach%2C%20no%20one%20does%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20on%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20times%20where%20people%20like%20to%20explore%20options%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20Chahal%20approached%20her%20directly%20for%20marriage%2C%20Dhanashree%20admitted%20that%20it%20left%20a%20big%20impression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20easy%20for%20everyone%20to%20explore%20options%2C%20meet%20more%20people%20socially.%20He%20was%20straight%20up%20like%20I%20want%20to%20marry%20you.%20I%20never%20had%20the%20pressure%20of%20getting%20married.%20I%20was%20very%20happy%20with%20my%20life%2C%20everything%20was%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689495420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fjvvmim4_chahal-and-dhanashree_625x300_16_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdidnt-know-who-yuzi-chahal-was-wife-d-had-no-clue-who-yuzi-chahal-was-wife-dhanashree-makes-candid-confessionhanashree-makes-candid-confession-4211787%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dhanashree%20Verma%20and%20Yuzvendra%20Chahal%20first%20started%20talking%20to%20each%20other%20virtually%20as%20the%20Indian%20cricketer%20approached%20her%20to%20take%20dance%20classes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdidnt-know-who-yuzi-chahal-was-wife-d-had-no-clue-who-yuzi-chahal-was-wife-dhanashree-makes-candid-confessionhanashree-makes-candid-confession-4211787%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdidnt-know-who-yuzi-chahal-was-wife-d-had-no-clue-who-yuzi-chahal-was-wife-dhanashree-makes-candid-confessionhanashree-makes-candid-confession-4211787%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fdidnt-know-who-yuzi-chahal-was-wife-d-had-no-cl