cap-mutual-funds-net-inflow-rs-11-000-cr-in-q1fy24-123071600238_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20At%20French%20President's%20Dinner%20For%20PM%20Modi%2C%20A%20%5C%22Jai%20Ho%5C%22%20Performance%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20two-day%20visit%20to%20France%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20attended%20a%20banquet%20dinner%20hosted%20by%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20at%20the%20Louvre%20Museum%20in%20Paris%20on%20Friday.%20The%20dinner%20was%20regarded%20as%20special%20for%20several%20reasons.%20It%20was%20held%20on%20the%20national%20day%20of%20France%20on%20July%2014%2C%20which%20is%20also%20known%20as%20Bastille%20Day.%20This%20was%20also%20the%20first%20time%20a%20banquet%20dinner%20was%20hosted%20at%20the%20Louvre%20Museum%20since%201953%20when%20Queen%20Elizabeth%20II%20was%20invited.%20Amid%20this%2C%20a%20video%20of%20the%20popular%20song%20%26quot%3BJai%20Ho%26quot%3B%20being%20played%20at%20the%20banquet%20dinner%20is%20going%20viral%20on%20the%20internet%20and%20the%20two%20leaders%20are%20seen%20enjoying%20the%20performance%20thoroughly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20video%2C%20a%20band%20is%20seen%20singing%20the%20Oscar-winning%20song%20by%20AR%20Rahman%20as%20Mr%20Macron%20and%20PM%20Modi%20watch%20the%20performance.%20Both%20of%20them%20are%20seen%20enjoying%20the%20song%20and%20also%20sharing%20smiles%20in%20between.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20French%20President%20is%20seen%20thumping%20the%20table%20as%20he%20enjoys%20the%20beats%20of%20the%20songs%2C%20Several%20people%20present%20at%20the%20venue%20are%20seen%20appreciating%20the%20performance.%20As%20per%20ANI%2C%20the%20song%20was%20played%20twice%20at%20the%20dinner.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20this%2C%20but%20the%20dinner%20menu%20also%20had%20a%20special%20gesture%20for%20PM%20Modi.%20It%20featured%20the%20Indian%20tricolour%20instead%20of%20the%20colours%20of%20the%20national%20flag%20of%20France.%20In%20addition%2C%20a%20vegetarian%20menu