%20the%20water%20levels%20within%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20water%20from%20flowing%20into%20the%20city%2C%20we%20have%20created%20a%20wall%20by%20stacking%20up%20sacks%2C%20said%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%2C%20Delhi's%20flood%20control%20and%20irrigation%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20said%20that%20Yamuna%20is%20receding%20slowly%20and%20the%20situation%20will%20normalise%20soon%20if%20there%20is%20no%20more%20heavy%20rain%20but%20added%20that%20the%20threat%20of%20flood%20is%20not%20over%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flooding%20hit%20Delhi%20following%20heavy%20rainfall%20across%20north%20India%2C%20which%20has%20killed%20dozens%20of%20people%20over%20the%20past%20week.%20The%20Yamuna%20spilled%20out%20onto%20roads%20surrounding%20Delhi's%20historic%20Red%20Fort%2C%20reclaiming%20its%20ancient%20flow%20path%2C%20while%20schools%2C%20colleges%2C%20and%20universities%20in%20the%20city%20are%20closed%20till%20Sunday.%20Some%20shops%20and%20businesses%20have%20also%20been%20shuttered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20people%20were%20moved%20from%20low-lying%20areas%20to%20temporary%20relief%20centers%20set%20up%20in%20schools%20and%20other%20buildings%2C%20with%20many%20people%20also%20taking%20refuge%20in%20tents%20and%20under%20flyovers.%20Some%20of%20the%20relief%20camps%20that%20the%20government%20had%20set%20up%20have%20now%20gone%20under%20water%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689488580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fjlvr4d4_delhi-flood_625x300_16_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhy-delhi-is-flooded-even-as-yamuna-gradually-recedes-4211826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Water%20levels%20of%20Yamuna%20are%20gradually%20receding%20but%20this%20hasn't%20had%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20the%20flooded%20Delhi%20streets.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nd