Fskynews-benjamin-netanyahu_6219997.jpg%3F20230716075028%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisraeli-prime-minister-benjamin-netanyahu-set-to-be-discharged-from-hospital-following-dehydration-12921676%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20has%20been%20released%20from%20hospital%20on%20Sunday%20after%20suffering%20from%20dehydration.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A47%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisraeli-prime-minister-benjamin-netanyahu-set-to-be-discharged-from-hospital-following-dehydration-12921676%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisraeli-prime-minister-benjamin-netanyahu-set-to-be-discharged-from-hospital-following-dehydration-12921676%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fisraeli-prime-minister-benjamin-netanyahu-set-to-be-discharged-from-hospital-following-dehydration-12921676%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Many%20Wonders%20of%20a%20Public%20Library%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16113818%2FDSC09401.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESaakhi%20is%20a%20Sunday%20column%20from%20Mrinal%20Pande%2C%20in%20which%20she%20writes%20of%20what%20she%20sees%20and%20also%20participates%20in.%20That%20has%20been%20her%20burden%20to%20bear%20ever%20since%20she%20embarked%20on%20a%20life%20as%20a%20journalist%2C%20writer%2C%20editor%2C%20author%20and%20as%20chairperson%20of%20Prasar%20Bharti.%20Her%20journey%20of%20being%20a%20witness-participant%20continues.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20I%20was%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20it%20was%20to%20check%20on%20my%20older%20sister%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20who%20had%20both%20faced%20serious%20health%20issues.%20Dehradun%20is%20no%20longer%20a%20town%20we%20knew%20as%20children%2C%20full%20of%20tree-lined%20lanes%2C%20large%20houses%20with%20well%20planted%20gardens%20and%20quaint%20markets%20with%20perfectly%20preserved%20old%20public%20schools%2C%20bakeries%20and%20a%20cantonment%20area.%20But%20it%20is%20still%20very%20nice.%20We%20still%20get%20a%20minimal%20sense%20of%20continuity%20in%20Doon.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20where%20my%20husband%20went%20to%20school%2C%20various%20grand%20aunts%20waited%20for%20us%20during%20summer%20breaks%20with%20welcoming%20arms%2C%20and%20some%20three%20decades%20ago%20my%20sister%20and%20her%20academic%20husband%20Dr%20B.K.%20Joshi%20set%20up%20home%20after%20he%20took%20early%20retirement%20from%20his%20job%20as%20a%20vice-chancellor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20always%20happens%20in%20close-knit%20families%2C%20as%20we%20were%20handed%20our%20steaming%20hot%20cups%2C%20we%20slipped%20backwards%20in%20time%20with%20old%20friends%20who%20had%20also%20relocated%20to%20Doon%2C%20like%20the%20poet%20Arvind%20Krishna%20Mehrotra.%20Then%20the%20talk%20veered%20into%20a%20discussion%20on%20Joshi%E2%80%99s%20pet%20project%20since%201998%20and%20my%20sister%E2%80%99s%20pet%20peeve%3A%20The%20Doon%20Library%20and%20Research%20Centre.%20Joshi%2C%20as%20a%20well-known%20academic%2C%20had%20continued%20his%20research%20work%20as%20a%20social%20scientist%20and%20had%20provided%20consultancy%20services%20to%20Save%20the%20Children%20and%20Unicef%20.%20My%20sister%20felt%20this%20was%20too%20much%20work%20for%20a%20frail%20man%20like%20him.%20Their%20squabbles%20were%20stuff%20of%20many%20family%20jokes%20and%20lore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20schooled%20in%20Mussoorie%2C%20my%20brother-in-law%20had%20selflessly%20devoted%20himself%20to%20the%20governments%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20new%20born%20state%20of%20Uttarakhand%20and%20when%20asked%20to%2C%20headed%20various%20committees%20on%20development%20and%20the%20changing%20ecology%20of%20Uttarakhand.%20He%20found%20that%20a%20town%20that%20had%20groomed%20and%20housed%20writers%20and%20poets%20like%20Vikram%20Seth%2C%20Amitav%20Ghosh%2C%20Nayantara%20Sehgal%2C%20Arvind%20Krishna%20Mehrotra%20and%20Allan%20Sealy%20did%20not%20have%20a%20public%20library.%20For%20his%20own%20projects%2C%20he%20had%20to%20go%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20LBS%20National%20Academy%20of%20Administration%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20sister%2C%20like%20the%20devoted%20and%20headstrong%20wife%20she%20is%2C%20pooh-poohed%20it%20as%20the%20mad%20obsession%20of%20an%20absent-minded%20professor.%20All%20siblings%20and%20their%20spouses%20were%20expected%20to%20take%20her%20side%20and%20talk%20him%20out%20of%20the%20idea.%20%E2%80%9CWho%20reads%20books%20anymore%3F%20You%20see%20all%20these%20moronic%20anchors%20on%20TV%20and%20party%20spokespersons%20on%20TV%20and%20YouTube%2C%20do%20you%20think%20they%20even%20touch%20books%3F%20Everyone%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20this%20passion%20for%20learning!%E2%80%9D%20Then%20she%E2%80%99d%20turn%20to%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CWho%20listens%20to%20me%20in%20this%20house%3F%20Even%20our%20son%20agrees%20with%20his%20Babba.%E2%80%9D%20The%20stubborn%20man%20with%20a%20gentle%20voice%20remonstrated%2C%20backed%20by%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20you%20see%2C%20I%20am%20giving%20the%20people%20what%20they%20did%20not%20know%20they%20needed!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20363px)%2085vw%2C%20363px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mrinal%20Pande%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22363%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783.jpg%20525w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F05103945%2FIMG_1783-246x300.jpg%20246w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-642789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22443%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20what%20about%20your%20own%20health%3F%20You%20are%20no%20spring%20chicken!%E2%80%9D%20my%20sister%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20routine%20answer%20was%20shot%20off%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20owe%20the%20State%20that%20enabled%20me%20and%20whose%20subsidies%20paid%20for%20my%20higher%20education%2C%20fixed%20my%20body%20each%20time%20I%20fell%20sick%20and%20paid%20my%20hospital%20bills.%20I%20am%20only%20trying%20to%20repay.%E2%80%9D%20My%20sister%20would%20pull%20her%20familiar%20bored%20face%20and%20say%20something%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20any%20argument%20like%20this%20to%20her%20lacked%20sense%20and%20remains%20a%20socio-liberal%20one.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20are%20a%20fine%20one%20to%20ask%20him%20not%20to%20care%20for%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20I%20yelled%20back%20at%20her%20once%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20you%E2%80%99ve%20been%20running%20a%20free%20school%20for%20construction%20site%20workers%E2%80%99%20children%20in%20your%20home%20for%20as%20many%20years!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shut%20her%20up%2C%20but%20not%20for%20too%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202006%2C%20Joshi%20had%20registered%20the%20library%20and%20framed%20a%20Memorandum%20of%20Association%20and%20a%20governing%20body%20comprising%20eminent%20persons%20and%20academics%20backed%20by%20his%20close%20friends%20Alan%20Sealy%2C%20Arvind%20Krishna%20Mehrotra%20and%20Surjit%20Das%2C%20the%20chief%20secretary.%20So%20now%20they%20had%20a%20registration%2C%20some%20money%20and%20a%20good%20librarian%2C%20but%20there%20was%20no%20place%20to%20start%20work.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EMil%20gaya%20koda%2C%20ab%20kya%20chahiye%20jean%20lagaam%20aur%20ghoda%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20have%20a%20whip%2C%20a%20saddle%20and%20the%20rein%2C%20who%20needs%20a%20horse%3F)%E2%80%9D%20he%20laughed%20as%20the%20team%20faced%20the%20toughest%20priority%20%E2%80%93%20to%20find%20a%20large%20place%20for%20the%20library%20to%20house%20the%20books%20and%20a%20large%20reading%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20buildings%20they%20found%20and%20liked%20had%20rentals%20the%20library%20could%20not%20afford.%20Some%20that%20were%20offered%20were%20far%20outside%20the%20town%20and%20the%20team%20felt%20that%20would%20defeat%20the%20very%20purpose%20of%20a%20public%20library%2C%20to%20be%20accessible%2C%20easy%20to%20locate%20and%20free.%20The%20thousands%20of%20aspirational%20but%20poor%20students%20and%20locals%20needed%20a%20library%20that%20became%20a%20home%20to%20them%2C%20an%20%3Cem%3Eadda%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20brainstorming%20and%20occasionally%20listening%20to%20mind-expanding%20lectures.%20Finally%2C%20a%20renovated%20building%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20town%20was%20made%20partially%20available%20to%20them.%20This%20spurred%20them%20to%20procure%20books%20and%20journals.%20The%20Education%20Directorate%20made%20the%20first%20donation%20of%20many%20rare%20books%20and%20some%20were%20purchased%20with%20the%20funds%20at%20their%20disposal.%20One%20minor%20problem%20remained%20%E2%80%93%20sharing%20the%20premises%20with%20a%20minor%20political%20party%E2%80%99s%20cacophonous%20office.%20The%20party%20had%20already%20used%20bullying%2C%20secrecy%20and%20outright%20arm-twisting%20to%20bag%20the%20largest%20room%20as%20a%20permanent%20%3Cem%3Edharna%20sthal%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20pandemic%20helped%20the%20library%20group%20get%20the%20space%20vacated%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16113909%2FDSCN1319.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16113909%2FDSCN1319.png%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16113909%2FDSCN1319-300x225.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-663429%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20Doon%20Library%20and%20Research%20Centre.%20Photo%3A%20Doon%20Library%20website%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20now%2C%20the%20library%20was%20attracting%20a%20large%20number%20of%20young%20regulars%2C%20especially%20students%20preparing%20for%20various%20competitive%20exams%20who%20had%20no%20one%20addressing%20their%20needs%20except%20some%20coaching%20centres%20that%20charged%20a%20huge%20fee.%20When%20the%20library%20began%20to%20keep%20popular%20books%20and%20material%20they%20could%20use%20only%20on%20the%20premises%2C%20the%20response%20was%20phenomenal.%20The%20youth%2C%20which%20also%20included%20many%20young%20women%20by%20now%2C%20were%20happy%20to%20sit%20outside%20on%20the%20lawns%20as%20the%20reading%20room%20filled%20up.%20But%20Joshi%20still%20felt%20they%20must%20offer%20more.%20He%20ordered%20multiple%20copies%20of%20popular%20journals%2C%20and%20helped%20by%20his%20devoted%20team%2C%20converted%20the%20existing%20stack%20rooms%20for%20books%20to%20another%20reading%20room.%20The%20numbers%20grew%20and%20discussion%20groups%20were%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20problems%20of%20mounting%20bills%20and%20water%20logging%20during%20monsoons%2C%20the%20library%20by%202017%20had%20the%20reputation%20of%20a%20serious%20quiet%20and%20accessible%20public%20space%20for%20book%20lovers%20and%20students.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20they%20started%20a%20series%20of%20events%20for%20which%20local%20writers%20and%20bureaucrats%20became%20his%20willing%20allies.%20They%20helped%20bring%20the%20library%20under%20the%20Uttaranchal%20Public%20Library%20Act%202005%2C%20which%20made%20it%20eligible%20to%20receive%20government%20grants.%20In%20February%202018%2C%20finally%20a%20major%20light%20was%20visible%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20long%20tunnel.%20The%20Airports%20Authority%20of%20India%20had%20sanctioned%20Rs%207.50%20crore%20for%20the%20building.%20Alongside%20this%2C%20the%20then%20chief%20secretary%20Utpal%20Singh%20identified%20a%20plot%20of%20land%20at%20Lansdowne%20Chowk%2C%20where%20a%20new%20building%20soon%20began%20to%20take%20shape.%20Meanwhile%20Joshi%2C%20who%20was%20by%20now%20over%2080%2C%20agreed%20at%20last%20with%20his%20spouse%20that%20all%20this%20hard%20work%20was%20taking%20a%20serious%20toll%20on%20his%20health.%20In%202022%2C%20he%20persuaded%20the%20general%20body%20to%20allow%20him%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20reins%20to%20a%20former%20chief%20secretary%2C%20N.%20Ravishankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20library%20by%20now%20has%2032%2C031%20books%20in%20both%20English%20and%20Hindi%20spanning%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20subjects%2C%20old%20gazetteers%2C%20colonial%20historiographies%20and%20administrative%20correspondence%20dating%20back%20to%20the%201850s.%20It%20has%204%2C829%20active%20members%20who%20on%20an%20average%20borrow%20a%20total%20of%20300-400%20books%20each%20month.%20The%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20has%20also%20chipped%20in%20by%20helping%20the%20library%20digitise%20and%20use%20an%20open-source%20library%20software%20(Koha)%20in%20the%20new%20building%20they%20have%20just%20shifted%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20building%20will%20have%20multiple%20uses.%20It%20will%20have%20place%20to%20expand%20with%20the%20times%20and%20also%20provide%20facilities%20to%20members%20like%20internet%20connectivity%2C%20spaces%20for%20holding%20seminars%20and%20exhibitions%2C%20and%20various%20galleries.%20The%20market%2C%20Joshi%20feels%2C%20may%20have%20no%20use%20for%20libraries%20today.%20Nor%20can%20a%20library%20experience%20be%20created%20online.%20But%20citizens%E2%80%99%20cooperation%20and%20a%20charming%20benign%20state%E2%80%99s%20help%2C%20rare%20though%20it%20is%2C%20can%20bring%20about%20miracles%20in%20the%20quality%20of%20public%20life.%20Libraries%20like%20the%20Doon%20Library%20are%20today%20filled%20with%20members%20and%20regulars%20because%20as%20the%20students%20told%20the%20staff%2C%20what%20a%20good%20library%20offers%20cannot%20be%20easily%20found%20elsewhere%3A%20an%20indoor%20public%20space%20in%20which%20you%20do%20not%20have%20to%20buy%20anything%20in%20order%20to%20stay%20and%20soak%20in%20the%20good%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20hierarchy%20of%20needs%20in%20a%20small%20young%20hill%20state%20like%20Uttarakhand%2C%20that%20are%20struggling%20to%20come%20up%20for%20air.%20Libraries%20may%20not%20figure%20in%20most%20priority%20lists%20like%20a%20big%20hospital%20or%20school%20classrooms%20do%2C%20but%20a%20public%20library%20will%20remain%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20the%20social%20reality%20of%20the%20state.%20It%20is%20the%20only%20place%2C%20Joshi%20says%20with%20a%20twinkle%2C%20that%20does%20not%20claim%20your%20vital%20data%20or%20your%20wallet.%20After%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20new%20building%20where%20a%20wheelchair-using%20Joshi%20received%20a%20standing%20ovation%20from%20the%20public%2C%20even%20my%20sister%20was%20moved.%20She%20knew%20he%20had%20been%20right%20of%20course%2C%20and%20we%20must%20all%20promote%20public%20libraries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20I%20must%20also%20defend%20my%20old%20man%20and%20guard%20his%20health%20like%20a%20dragon%20even%20if%20he%20will%20not!%20Call%20me%20a%20shrew%20if%20you%20will%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20to%20us%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20you%20must%20agree%20I%20am%20a%20good%20guard%20for%20those%20who%20guard%20public%20spaces!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWho%20is%20one%20to%20disagree%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fmrinal-pande%5C%22%3EMrinal%20Pande%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20writer%20and%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689487831000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16113818%2FDSC09401.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fthe-many-wonders-of-a-public-library%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20que