k%20that%20ensures%20equal%20rights%20for%20all%2C%20regardless%20of%20religion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deliberations%20on%20Saturday%20saw%20the%20participation%20of%20key%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20India%2C%20the%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20representatives%20from%20high%20courts%2C%20Vice%20Chancellors%20of%20law%20universities%2C%20legal%20luminaries%2C%20and%20civil%20society%20organisations%2C%20reported%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ER.%20Venkataramani%2C%20the%20Attorney-General%20of%20India%2C%20highlighted%20the%20need%20for%20reforming%20and%20strengthening%20the%20institution%20of%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20(Venkataramani)%20emphasised%20the%20following%20points%3Aequal%20regard%20for%20men%20and%20women%2C%20equal%20status%20for%20men%20and%20women%2C%20equality%20of%20processes%20ensuring%20dignity%20in%20entering%20and%20exiting%20marital%20relationships%20irrespective%20of%20religion%2C%E2%80%9D%20ANI%20reported%2C%20quoting%20an%20NCW%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NCW%20also%20said%20that%20the%20deliberations%20also%20included%20consultations%20on%20reforming%20divorce%20as%20a%20judicial%20process%2C%20with%20exception%20to%20divorce%20through%20mutual%20consent%2C%20and%20the%20need%20to%20reform%20inheritance%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2022nd%20Law%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20notification%20last%20month%20came%20despite%20the%2021st%20commission%20suggesting%20in%202018%20that%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20%E2%80%9Cis%20neither%20necessary%20nor%20desirable%20at%20this%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20more%20than%20three%20years%20have%20lapsed%20from%20the%20date%20of%20issuance%20of%20the%20said%20consultation%20paper%2C%20bearing%20in%20mind%20the%20relevance%20and%20importance%20of%20the%20subject%20and%20also%20the%20various%20court%20orders%20on%20the%20subject%2C%20the%2022nd%20Law%20Commission%20considered%20it%20expedient%20to%20deliberate%20afresh%20over%20the%20subject%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20commission%E2%80%99s%20notification%20said%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Faimplb-calls-law-commissions-proposal-to-seek-fresh-views-on-ucc-politically-motivated%5C%22%3Ethe%20All%20India%20Muslim%20Personal%20Law%20Board%20opposed%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20representation%20to%20the%20Law%20Commission%20and%20called%20the%20exercise%20%E2%80%9Cpolitically%20motivated%E2%80%9D%20to%20divide%20the%20country%20on%20religious%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20various%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felection-rhetoric-or-real-plan-opposition-raises-questions-as-bjp-broaches-ucc-yet-again%5C%22%3Eopposition%20parties%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnda-partners-in-northeast-oppose-bjps-push-for-uniform-civil-code%5C%22%3ENDA%20allies%2C%20have%20also%20opposed%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20move%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689484984000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F16104944%2FF1D46RJaEAEYVGM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fncw-says-non-codified-nature-of-muslim-personal-law-poses-challenges-to-women%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20National%20Commission%20for%20Women%20said%20that%20absence%20of%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20has%20perpetuated%20inequalities%20and%20inconsistencies%20in%20the%20country%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fncw-says-non-codified-nature-of-muslim-personal-law-poses-challenges-to-women%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Maaveran'%20box%20office%20collection%20day%202%22%