iled%20for%2011%20years%20after%20they%20enslaved%20and%20left%20a%20disabled%20man%20in%20filthy%20conditions%2C%20as%20per%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fcrime%2Fsussex-disabled-man-wife-partner-jailed-b2375773.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndependent%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20a%20trial%20at%20Portsmouth%20Court%2C%20Sarah%20Somerset-How%20and%20George%20Webb%20were%20found%20guilty%20of%20holding%20her%20husband%20Tom%20Somerset-How%20in%20slavery%20and%20three%20counts%20of%20mistreatment%20by%20a%20care%20worker%20between%202016%20and%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caretaker%2C%20who%20was%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20the%20woman%2C%20was%20also%20convicted%20of%20%26quot%3Bcausing%20actual%20bodily%20harm%26quot%3B%20to%20Mr%20Somerset-How.%20The%2040-year-old%20man%20was%20suffering%20from%20cerebral%20palsy%20and%20used%20an%20electric%20wheelchair%2C%20and%20was%20bedridden%20and%20malnourished.%20He%20was%20allegedly%20mistreated%20and%20abused%20by%20the%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20outlet%2C%20Mr%20Somerset-How%20recalled%20in%20court%20how%20horrified%20he%20was%20to%20learn%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20Mr%20Webb%20%26quot%3Bdespised%26quot%3B%20him%20and%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bfive-year%20plan%26quot%3B%20to%20continue%20taking%20advantage%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20extent%20of%20the%20betrayal%20was%20hard%20to%20bear%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20I%20felt%20I%20was%20just%20being%20kept%20alive%2C%20when%20the%20reality%20sank%20in%2C%20this%20really%20was%20my%20life%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20end%20it%20all%2C%20I%20couldn't%20even%20manage%20that.%20I%20feel%20like%20Sarah%20has%20ruined%20me%20for%20anyone%20else%2C%20I%20feel%20abandoned%20like%20I%20was%20pushed%20to%20one%20side%2C%20I%20couldn't%20trust%20the%20one%20person%20who%20should%20have%20been%20on%20my%20side%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20He%20claimed%20he%20had%20been%20concerned%20he%20would%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20reconnect%20with%20his%20family%2C%20particularly%20his%20mother%2C%20whom%20he%20had%20alienated%20while%20being%20%26quot%3Bmonitored%26quot%3B%20by%20his%20wife%20and%20Mr%20Webb%20to%20make%20sure%20he%20did%20not%20reveal%20their%20abuse%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20explain%20to%20her%20what%20was%20happening%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20better%20they%20stay%20away%2C%20protect%20them%20from%20George%20and%20the%20nuclear%20bomb%20that%20was%20his%20anger%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20court.%20Mr%20Somerset-How%20stated%20that%20although%20he%20is%20currently%20residing%20in%20a%20care%20facility%2C%20he%20wishes%20to%20live%20more%20independently.%20He%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20emotions%20he%20used%20to%20feel%20during%20his%20treatment%20and%20said%20that%20he%20would%20scream%20in%20his%20care%20facility%20room%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Bprimal%20scream%26quot%3B%20until%20he%20lost%20his%20voice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20Judge%20William%20Ashworth%20appreciated%20the%20man%20for%20his%20courage%20and%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20find%20as%20fact%20of%20which%20I%20am%20sure%20that%20Tom%20Somerset-How%20was%20held%20in%20slavery%20for%20at%20least%20two%20years%20and%20eight%20months%2C%20kept%20in%20bed%2C%20deprived%20of%20adequate%20food%20or%20water%2C%20kept%20away%20from%20his%20family%20with%20the%20curtains%20drawn%2C%20frequently%20in%20his%20own%20urine%20and%20excrement%2C%20unwashed%20and%20unkempt.%26quot%3B%20He%20stated%20that%20Mr%20Somerset-How%20was%20%26quot%3Bdenigrated%20by%20the%20defendants%20and%20humiliated%20and%20his%20requests%20to%20go%20to%20the%20toilet%20scorned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20added%20that%20the%20man%20has%20suffered%20%26quot%3Bserious%20psychological%20harm%26quot%3B.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20had%20lost%20any%20independence%20and%20was%20treated%20like%20a%20cow%20to%20be%20milked.%20But%2C%20in%20our%20society%2C%20a%20cow%20is%20protected%20by%20minimum%20standards%20of%20husbandry%20and%20not%20even%20these%20were%20afforded%20to%20Tom%20by%20his%20carers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689482220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Frj9ju81_aa_625x300_16_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwife-caretaker-of-disabled-man-jailed-in-uk-for-slaving-and-starving-him-for-4-years-4211685%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mr%20Somerset-How%20recalled%20in%20court%20how%20horrified%20he%20was%20to%20learn%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20Mr%20Webb%20%26quot%3Bdespised%26quot%3B%20him%20and%20had%20a%20%26quot%3Bfive-year%20plan%26quot%3B%20to%20continue%20taking%20advantage%20of%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwife-caretaker-of-disabled-man-jailed-in-uk-for-slaving-and-starving-him-for-4-years-4211685%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwife-caretaker-of-disabled-man-jailed-in-uk-for-slaving-and-starving-him-for-4-years-4211685%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwife-caretaker-of-disabled-man-jailed-in-uk-for-slaving-and-starving-him-for-4-years-4211685%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Singapore%E2%80%99s%20widening%20corruption%20probe%3A%20What%20you%20need%20to%20know%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689482205000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101794938%2Cimgsize-273700.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsingapores-widening-corruption-probe-what-you-need-to-know%2Farticleshow%2F101794950.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F101794950.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%