0After%20discussions%20between%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20President%20Sheikh%20Mohamed%20bin%20Zayed%20Al%20Nahyan%2C%20India%20and%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20jointly%20announced%20on%20Saturday%2C%20July%2015%2C%20the%20commencement%20of%20a%20trade%20settlement%20using%20their%20respective%20local%20currencies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Further%2C%20the%20Indian%20Unified%20Payments%20Interface%20will%20be%20interconnected%20with%20the%20Gulf%20kingdom%E2%80%99s%20Instant%20Payment%20Platform%20(IPP).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Indian%20PM%20was%20in%20UAE%20for%20a%20day-long%20visit%20from%20Paris.%20He%20left%20for%20New%20Delhi%20after%20talks%20with%20the%20UAE%20leadership.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20and%20the%20Central%20Bank%20of%20the%20UAE%20Khaled%20Mohamed%20Balama%20have%20signed%20two%20Memoranda%20of%20Understanding%20(MoUs).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EI%20had%20the%20pleasure%20of%20welcoming%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40narendramodi%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20Abu%20Dhabi%20today.%20We%20discussed%20the%20ongoing%20progress%20of%20our%20bilateral%20ties%2C%20our%20shared%20interest%20in%20promoting%20sustainable%20global%20growth%2C%20and%20ways%20to%20further%20boost%20collaboration%20between%20our%20countries%20%26amp%3B%20our%20people.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FJ7bqEW76HA%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FJ7bqEW76HA%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20%D9%85%D8%AD%D9%85%D8%AF%20%D8%A8%D9%86%20%D8%B2%D8%A7%D9%8A%D8%AF%20(%40MohamedBinZayed)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMohamedBinZayed%2Fstatus%2F1680165766539231233%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20aims%20to%20establish%20a%20framework%20that%20encourages%20the%20utilisation%20of%20local%20currencies%2C%20specifically%20the%20Indian%20rupee%20(INR)%20and%20the%20UAE%20Dirham%20(AED)%2C%20for%20cross-border%20transactions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20MoU%20focuses%20on%20cooperation%20for%20interlinking%20their%20payment%20and%20messaging%20systems.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20primary%20objective%20of%20the%20MoU%20on%20establishing%20a%20framework%20for%20the%20use%20of%20local%20currencies%20is%20to%20implement%20a%20Local%20Currency%20Settlement%20System%20(LCSS)%20that%20promotes%20bilateral%20use%20of%20the%20INR%20and%20AED%20for%20transactions%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%20emphasised%20that%20the%20agreement%20for%20trade%20settlement%20in%20the%20currencies%20of%20both%20nations%20exemplifies%20the%20robust%20economic%20cooperation%20and%20mutual%20trust%20shared%20by%20India%20and%20the%20UAE.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThree%20transformative%20MoUs%20were%20exchanged%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1%EF%B8%8F%E2%83%A3%20MoU%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRBI%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RBI%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26amp%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcentralbankuae%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40centralbankuae%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20framework%20to%20promote%20the%20use%20of%20local%20currencies%20(INR%20%E2%80%93%20AED)%20for%20cross-border%20transactions%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2%EF%B8%8F%E2%83%A3%20MoU%20between%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRBI%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40RBI%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26amp%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fcentralbankuae%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40centralbankuae%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20bilateral%20cooperation%20on%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FITqvPKGGKq%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FITqvPKGGKq%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Arindam%20Bagchi%20(%40MEAIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMEAIndia%2Fstatus%2F1680173639868755969%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2015%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20public%20remarks%2C%20Modi%20highlighted%20that%20trade%20between%20India%20and%20the%20UAE%20has%20experienced%20a%20notable%2020%25%20growth%20since%20the%20signing%20of%20the%20Comprehensive%20Economic%20Partnership%20Agreement%20in%20the%20previous%20year%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20Memoranda%20of%20Understanding%20(MoUs)%20between%20the%20central%20banks%2C%20the%20Indian%20PM%C2%A0%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20very%20important%20aspect%20of%20India-UAE%20cooperation.%20It%20paves%20the%20way%20for%20enhanced%20economic%20collaboration%20and%20will%20make%20international%20financial%20interactions%20simpler%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20ministry%20of%20Education%20and%20Abu%20Dhabi%E2%80%99s%20Education%20and%20Knowledge%20Department%20(ADEK)%20also%20signed%20an%20MoU%20to%20establish%20a%20campus%20of%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%20Delhi%20in%20the%20Gulf%20country.%20This%20agreement%20marks%20the%20second%20IIT%20to%20announce%20the%20establishment%20of%20an%20offshore%20campus%2C%20following%20IIT%20Madras%20in%20Tanzania.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689435412000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023